ssue%20that%20tends%20to%20resurface.%20During%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20in%202021%2C%20her%20insecurities%20resurfaced%20when%20she%20experienced%20a%20relationship%20break-up.%20She%20attributes%20it%20to%20her%20plus-sized%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mental%20turmoil%20hampered%20her%20professional%20work%20and%20she%20started%20to%20journal%20to%20get%20out%20of%20that%20sinking%20feeling.%20Things%20took%20a%20dramatic%20turn%20when%20a%20modeling%20agency%20noticed%20her%20self-styled%20photos%20on%20Instagram%20and%20offered%20her%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20a%20seasoned%20model%2C%20Sharma%20talks%20about%20how%20fashion%20has%20given%20her%20more%20than%20money%20could%20measure.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20made%20me%20appreciate%20myself%2C%20given%20me%20self-esteem%20and%20pride.%20Today%2C%20I%20am%20a%20role%20model%20for%20many%20plus-sized%20women%20and%20I%20get%20messages%20where%20they%20say%20that%20they%20have%20been%20inspired%20to%20wear%20swimwear%20because%20of%20me%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125136%2Fkhushboo_2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125136%2Fkhushboo_2.jpg%20683w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125136%2Fkhushboo_2-200x300.jpg%20200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678005%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKhushboo%20Sharma.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20thriving%20in%20her%20newfound%20self-love%2C%20Sharma%20rues%20the%20fact%20that%20not%20enough%20is%20being%20done%20to%20increase%20the%20representation%20of%20alternate%20beauties%20in%20the%20Indian%20fashion%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProper%20scouting%20is%20not%20done%20for%20the%20plus-sized%20community%2C%20and%20only%20the%20models%20who%20had%20begun%20the%20diversity%20movement%20end%20up%20getting%20all%20the%20spots.%20The%20new%20girls%20are%20hardly%20featured.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20attempt%20to%20build%20and%20empower%20a%20community%20for%20upcoming%20faces%20and%20the%20same%20faces%20keep%20getting%20the%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharma%20claims%20to%20have%20built%20a%20plus-sized%20community%20of%205%2C000%20women%20who%20aspire%20to%20work%20in%20the%20fashion%20industry.%20Sharma%20is%20also%20proud%20that%20her%20peers%20from%20her%20hometown%20have%20followed%20in%20her%20footsteps%20in%20owning%20their%20bodies%20and%20aspiring%20for%20a%20modelling%20career.%20%E2%80%9CBrands%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhouseofsoho.in%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3EHouse%20of%20Soho%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsajke.in%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3ESajke%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20some%20of%20my%20hometown%20brands%20featuring%20plus-sized%20models%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGlorification%20of%20beauty%20that%20often%20adheres%20to%20western%20standards%20leads%20to%20a%20huge%20section%20of%20insecure%20and%20neglected%20aspirants.%20India%E2%80%99s%20obsession%20with%20fair%20skin%20is%20a%20well-known%20fact.%20Due%20to%20pressures%20from%20a%20liberated%20feminist%20audience%2C%20Hindustan%20Unilever%E2%80%99s%20popular%20skin%20lightening%20cream%20%E2%80%98Fair%20%26amp%3B%20Lovely%E2%80%99%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ffair-and-lovely-hindustan-unilever%5C%22%3Ehad%20to%20rebrand%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20product%20to%20%E2%80%98Glow%20%26amp%3B%20Lovely%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESangeeta%20Gharu%2C%20a%20dusky%20beauty%20from%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Jodhpur%2C%20has%20a%20similar%20story.%20She%20was%20greatly%20stirred%20when%20she%20saw%20the%202008%20Bollywood%20blockbuster%20film%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFashion_(2008_film)%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFashion%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20star-spangled%20movie%20directed%20by%20Madhur%20Bhandarkar%20that%20dealt%20with%20the%20darker%20sides%20of%20the%20Indian%20fashion%20industry%20and%20how%20models%20fight%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20I%20first%20saw%20tall%2C%20lanky%2C%20dark-skinned%20models%20and%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gharu%2C%20who%20has%20been%20chasing%20her%20dreams%20across%20Jodhpur%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20finally%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20home%20to%20Bollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%20years%20of%20gruelling%20hard%20work%20punctuated%20by%20painful%20rejections%20due%20to%20her%20dark%20skin%20tone.%20She%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20credit%20to%20her%20mentor%20for%20counselling%20her.%20She%20was%20taught%20to%20first%20accept%20herself%20as%20beautiful%20before%20expecting%20recruiters%20to%20see%20the%20beauty%20in%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20every%20dark-skinned%20model%20out%20there%2C%20to%20love%20yourself%20and%20work%20hard%20%E2%80%93%20you%20will%20definitely%20succeed!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gharu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20fashion%20is%20still%20suffering%20from%20the%20patriarchal%20mindset%20where%20the%20male%20gaze%20allows%20only%20fair%2C%20slim%2C%20and%20tall%20models%20to%20be%20appreciated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20beauty%20standards%20in%20fashion%20are%20just%20the%20reflection%20of%20the%20beauty%20mindsets%20of%20all%20women.%20They%20are%20increasingly%20getting%20Botox%20to%20fix%20their%20noses%2C%20lips%2C%20faces%2C%20etc.%20They%20do%20it%20because%20they%20think%20it%20will%20earn%20them%20more%20love%20and%20%E2%80%98likes%E2%80%99%20on%20social%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Geetanjali%20Adhikari%2C%20a%20model%20from%20Delhi%2C%20whose%20fashion%20journey%20is%20one%20from%20facing%20fat-shaming%20to%20gaining%20acceptance%20and%20ultimately%20achieving%20industry%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20consider%20myself%20very%20lucky%20for%20being%20a%20plus-sized%20model.%20The%20body%20I%20was%20stigmatised%20for%2C%20is%20now%20celebrated.%20But%20I%20feel%20sorry%20for%20the%20big%20curvy%20girls%20who%20are%20still%20struggling%20within%20their%20bodies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flgbtqia%2Ffashionably-queer-what-does-fashion-mean-to-indias-queer-persons%5C%22%3EFashionably%20Queer%3A%20What%20Does%20Fashion%20Mean%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20Queer%20Persons%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETokenism%20in%20the%20fashion%20industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Luna%2C%20a%20transgender%20model%20and%20drag%20queen%2C%20the%20concept%20or%20idea%20of%20fashion%20is%20inclusive%20but%20the%20business%20of%20fashion%20may%20not%20be%20so.%20She%20says%20that%20tokenism%20continues%20to%20exist%20in%20Indian%20fashion%20despite%20significant%20strides%20having%20been%20made%20in%20inclusion%20and%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20business%20unfortunately%20has%20been%20run%20by%20men%20who%20have%20instilled%20their%20biases.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20am%20extremely%20thankful%20for%20social%20media%20because%20ten%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20imagined%20myself%20where%20I%20am%20today.%20I%20always%20thought%20fashion%20was%20not%20for%20me.%20Now%2C%20when%20I%20am%20in%20a%20room%20with%20people%20I%20have%20grown%20up%20idolising%2C%20it%20hits%20differently%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToshada%20Uma%2C%20who%20is%204%E2%80%999%E2%80%9D%20tall%2C%20has%20lost%20count%20of%20runway%20shows%20she%20has%20walked%20while%20wearing%20shoes%20that%20are%202-4%20sizes%20above%20hers.%20Her%20height%20is%20well%20below%20the%20conventional%20average.%20She%20remembers%20how%2C%20on%20multiple%20instances%2C%20her%20colleagues%20asked%20her%20what%20she%20did%20for%20a%20living.%20It%20sounded%20like%20they%20doubted%20if%20she%20belonged%20to%20the%20same%20set%2C%20got%20the%20same%20pay%2C%20and%20worked%20the%20same%20hours%20as%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20makes%20one%20think%20if%20things%20would%20be%20any%20different%20if%20the%20industry%20hired%20diverse%20models%20not%20just%20for%20some%20brownie%20points%20but%20because%20they%20genuinely%20believed%20it%20was%20important%20to%20represent%20various%20features%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20says%2C%20citing%20the%20common%20practice%20of%20tokenist%20inclusion%20versus%20an%20organic%20attempt%20to%20change%20the%20culture%20of%20recruiting%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharma%20considers%20the%20plus-sized%20fashion%20industry%20in%20India%20to%20be%20dysfunctional.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20clothes%20that%20are%20meant%20for%20us%20are%20unattractive%20and%20have%20no%20sense%20of%20creativity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20narrative%20that%20attempts%20to%20increase%20representation%20on%20the%20ramp%20are%20much%20more%20cosmetic%20than%20constructive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20pretentious%20malpractices%2C%20she%20says%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20major%20fashion%20events%20is%20known%20for%20giving%20out%20generic%20casting%20calls%20that%20encourage%20models%20of%20all%20looks%2C%20genders%2C%20and%20ethnicities%20to%20upload%20their%20photos%20and%20videos%20with%20the%20event%20hashtag.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20bother%20to%20see%20these%20videos%20that%20are%20uploaded%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20lived%20experience.%20We%20are%20ready%20to%20struggle%20for%20our%20spots%2C%20but%20giving%20us%20false%20hopes%20is%20just%20cruel%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20fashion%20diversity%20landscape%20is%20slowly%20evolving.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFashion%20designer%20Sabyasachi%20Mukherjee%20has%20on%20many%20occasions%20set%20high%20benchmarks%20for%20inclusion%20and%20diversity%20in%20Indian%20fashion.%20From%20introducing%20plus-sized%20models%20to%20giving%20opportunities%20to%20unconventional%20beauties%2C%20Mukherjee%20has%20made%20a%20name%20for%20his%20originality.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatimes.com%2Ftrending%2Fsocial-relevance%2Fsabyasachi-faces-backlash-over-sad-looking-model-599055.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSabyasachi%2520campaign%2520trolled%2520for%2520model%2520appearing%2520sad%2C-sabyasachiofficialVerified%26amp%3Btext%3DAlthough%2520it%2527s%2520not%2520exactly%2520common%2Crecent%2520campaigns%2520looked%2520particularly%2520sad.%5C%22%3Erecent%20controversy%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20he%20was%20trolled%20for%20an%20unsmiling%20model%2C%20also%20demonstrates%20his%20bold%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20designers%20who%20have%20done%20considerable%20work%20in%20increasing%20marginalised%20representation%20in%20Indian%20fashion%20include%20Manish%20Malhotra%2C%20Shivan%20and%20Narresh%2C%20Kunal%20Rawal%2C%20and%20Pallavi%20Mohan.%20Brands%20like%20Freakins%2C%20Zivame%2C%20Puma%2C%20Nykaa%2C%20Titan%20Raga%2C%20Vulgar%2C%20Fenty%2C%20Yeezy%2C%20and%20others%2C%20have%20joined%20the%20inclusivity%20bandwagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGauthami%20Jeji%2C%20a%20bisexual%20Indian%20model%20with%20vitiligo%20skin%20disorder%2C%20says%20that%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20was%20a%20watershed%20moment%20in%20Indian%20fashion.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20the%20stagnation%20in%20fashion%20standards%20and%20audience%20boredom%20prompted%20designers%2C%20producers%2C%20and%20agencies%20to%20explore%20new%20looks.%20Her%20skin%20condition%20has%20been%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise%2C%20leading%20to%20casting%20calls%20since%20she%20was%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVitiligo%20has%20certainly%20given%20me%20an%20edge%20but%20my%20position%20in%20the%20industry%20will%20be%20sustained%20because%20I%20am%20very%20good%20at%20what%20I%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20She%20further%20points%20out%20the%20need%20for%20honest%20representation.%20She%20adds%20that%20celebrating%20diversity%20and%20capitalising%20on%20a%20disorder%20are%20two%20very%20different%20things.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20faced%20tokenism%20personally%20%E2%80%93%20for%20example%2C%20for%20one%20shoot%20they%20take%20unique%20models%20and%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20employ%20them%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJeji%20believes%20that%20for%20things%20to%20change%2C%20the%20marginalised%20representation%20must%20be%20honest%20and%20transparent.%20Only%20then%20can%20beauty%20adapt%20to%20new%20standards%20organically.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125742%2Fgauthami_2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22933%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125742%2Fgauthami_2.jpg%20933w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125742%2Fgauthami_2-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03125742%2Fgauthami_2-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678006%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22933%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGauthami%20Jeji.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20see%20a%20world%20where%20models%20are%20called%20models%2C%20not%20plus-sized%20or%20trans%20models.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20call%20doctors%20plus-sized%20doctors%2C%20do%20we%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Sharma%2C%20the%20solution%20lies%20in%20raising%20awareness%20about%20body%20positivity%20and%20highlighting%20inspiring%20stories%20about%20fashion%20professionals%20who%20have%20overcome%20biases%20and%20are%20successful%20irrespective%20of%20how%20they%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUma%20looks%20forward%20to%20fashion%20being%20recontextualized%20as%20just%20another%20career%20path%2C%20and%20not%20a%20tool%20for%20cosmetic%20validation.%20Attaching%20glamour%20and%20self-worth%20to%20fashion%20makes%20it%20exploitative%20and%20unnecessarily%20overrated.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20good%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20only%20validation%20we%20need%20is%20our%20own.%20If%20modelling%20is%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%2C%20give%20it%20your%20100%25%2C%20confidently.%20If%20it%20works%20out%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20great%2C%20if%20it%20does%20not%2C%20keep%20your%20options%20open!%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ci%3ESreemanti%20Sengupta%20is%20a%20Kolkata-based%20freelance%20writer%2C%20poet%2C%20and%20media%20studies%20lecturer.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696320008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03130652%2Fimage-1369.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fbody-positivity-is-the-solution-to-tokenist-inclusion-in-the-indian-fashion-industry-say-models%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20fashion%20is%20still%20suffering%20from%20the%20patriarchal%20mindset%20where%20the%20male%20gaze%20allows%20only%20fair%2C%20slim%2C%20and%20tall%20models%20to%20be%20appreciated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fbody-positivity-is-the-solution-to-tokenist-inclusion-in-the-indian-fashion-industry-say-models%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Jimny%20tastefully%20modified%20into%20Mercedes-Benz%20G-Wagen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publ