%20of%20the%20Indian%20Association%20of%20People%20and%20its%20lawyer%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20the%20NIA%20sleuths.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20the%20officers.%20They%20had%20flown%20down%2C%20along%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epanch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20witnesses.%20But%20the%20local%20police%20were%20not%20informed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suresh%20said.%20The%20local%20police%2C%20Suresh%20says%2C%20joined%20much%20later.%20From%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20the%20NIA%20seized%20his%20phone%20and%20a%2012-page%20pamphlet%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20War%20Group%2C%20dating%20back%20to%201993.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuresh%20says%20for%20the%20longest%20period%2C%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20raid%20and%20the%20exact%20case%20in%20connection%20with%20which%20it%20was%20being%20conducted.%20The%20NIA%20later%20informed%20him%20that%20the%20ongoing%20raids%20were%20a%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CMunchingiputtu%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20conspiracy%20case%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20in%20connection%20with%20which%20similar%20raids%20were%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20residences%20of%20many%20rights%20activists%20and%20academics%20in%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuresh%20was%20served%20a%20notice%20under%20section%20160%20of%20the%20CrPC%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20be%20present%20before%20the%20NIA%20as%20a%20witness.%20This%2C%20Suresh%20points%20out%2C%20is%20both%20%E2%80%9Cunlawful%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunethical%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20counsel%20for%20many%20persons%20named%20in%20the%20case.%20I%20represent%20them%20in%20the%20high%20court%20and%20now%20the%20NIA%20wants%20me%20to%20appear%20before%20them%20as%20a%20witness%20in%20the%20same%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suresh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20a%20phone%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20lawyer%20has%20been%20named%20an%20accused%20or%20asked%20to%20be%20a%20witness%20in%20the%20same%20case%20they%20have%20appeared%20as%20counsel%20in%2C%20before%20a%20court.%20Surendra%20Gadling%2C%20a%20Nagpur-based%20lawyer%20and%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20was%20also%20made%20an%20accused%20in%20one%20of%20the%20cases%20in%20which%20he%20had%20defended%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20conflict-affected%20Vidarbha%20region%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHRF%20functionaries%20targeted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%2062%20locations%20raided%2C%2053%20are%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20nine%20are%20in%20Telangana.%20Along%20with%20the%20raids%20on%20October%202%2C%20the%20NIA%20also%20arrested%20one%20Chandra%20Narasimhulu%2C%20allegedly%20a%20state%20executive%20committee%20member%20of%20the%20Pragathiseela%20Karmika%20Samakya%20(PKS)%2C%20an%20alleged%20front%20organisation%20of%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist).%20Narasimhulu%20was%20arrested%20from%20Satya%20Sai%20district%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Along%20with%20his%20arrest%2C%20the%20NIA%20has%20claimed%20to%20have%20found%20a%20pistol%2C%2014%20rounds%20of%20ammunition%2C%20and%20Rs%2013%20lakhs%20in%20a%20case%20from%20another%20spot%20in%20Kadapa%20district.%20Maoist%20literature%20and%20pamphlets%20were%20also%20seized%2C%20the%20NIA%20has%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20those%20raided%20were%20unsure%20if%20they%20are%20being%20looked%20at%20as%20suspects%20or%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20house%20of%20K.%20Sudha%2C%20a%20state%20executive%20committee%20member%20of%20Human%20Rights%20Forum%2C%20was%20also%20raided.%20Sudha%2C%20who%20reaches%20at%20a%20state%20law%20university%2C%20said%20the%20NIA%20has%20taken%20her%20phone%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20raids%20took%20place%20at%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20V.S.%20Krishna%2C%20the%20convener%20of%20the%20HRF%E2%80%99s%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%20units%20reached%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20residence.%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20house%20was%20raided%20in%202021%20in%20the%20same%20case.%20Krishna%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20got%20calls%20from%20two%20other%20HRF%20members%2C%20who%20said%20that%20the%20NIA%20broke%20into%20their%20houses%20because%20they%20were%20not%20home%20when%20officials%20arrived.%20%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20contacting%20other%20members.%20When%20Sudha%20did%20not%20pick%20up%20the%20call%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20NIA%20had%20reached%20her%20place%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20two%20other%20person%E2%80%99s%20whose%20houses%20were%20raided%20when%20they%20were%20away%20are%20HRF%E2%80%99s%20AP%20state%20general%20secretary%20Y.%20Rajesh%20in%20Amalapuram%20and%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20state%20vice-president%20K.V.%20Jagannadha%20Rao%20in%20Srikakulam.%20Rajesh%2C%20who%20was%20on%20his%20way%20back%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%20when%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20him%20late%20on%20October%202%2C%20said%20that%20the%20NIA%20contacted%20him%20a%20little%20before%206%20am.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20came%20with%20a%20notice%20under%20Section%20165%20(2)%20of%20the%20CrPc%2C%20which%20authorised%20them%20to%20search%20the%20premise.%20Some%20of%20my%20neighbours%20went%20to%20my%20place%20and%20the%20NIA%20conducted%20the%20raid%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajesh%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20NIA%20has%20not%20made%20any%20seizures%20from%20his%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBooks%2C%20vernacular%20literature%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20from%20another%20HRF%20functionary%E2%80%99s%20place%2C%20the%20NIA%20has%20picked%20up%20over%2060%20books.%20Sudha%2C%20who%20shared%20information%20about%20the%20raid%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20basically%20picked%20up%20every%20book%20and%20document%20that%20had%20red%20font%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20said%20the%20officers%20did%20not%20know%20to%20read%20Telugu.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20books%20and%20our%20write-ups%20are%20in%20the%20local%20language.%20They%20mindlessly%20picked%20things%20up%20and%20later%20call%20it%20incriminating%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20HRF%20and%20IAPL%2C%20houses%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Civil%20Liberties%20Committee%20(CLC)%2C%20the%20Committee%20for%20the%20Release%20of%20Political%20Prisoners%20(CRPP)%2C%20and%20the%20Revolutionary%20Writers%20Association%20(RWA)%2C%20were%20also%20raided%20among%20others.%20The%20NIA%20has%20accused%20veteran%20rights%20activists%20and%20organisations%20of%20acting%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfronts%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20organisation%2C%20banned%20in%202009.%20This%20claim%20has%20been%20vehemently%20opposed%20by%20rights%20organisations.%20HRF%20has%20called%20the%20NIA%E2%80%99s%20claim%20%E2%80%9Ca%20plain%20canard%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CSeeking%20to%20criminalise%20our%20human%20rights%20activity%20will%20never%20succeed.%20HRF%20is%20not%20an%20appendage%20of%20the%20Maoists%20or%20any%20other%20political%20party.%20HRF%20was%20formed%20on%20October%2011%2C%201998%20and%20we%20have%20turned%2025%20this%20month.%20We%20shall%20persist%20in%20spreading%20a%20human%20rights%20culture%20in%20society%20with%20the%20certitude%20that%20a%20broad-based%20and%20truly%20independent%20human%20rights%20movement%20is%20desirable%20and%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20HRF%20said%2C%20in%20a%20press%20statement%20released%20earlier%20today%2C%20October%203.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20locations%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20subjected%20to%20raids%20are%20in%20Guntur%2C%20Palanadu%2C%20Vijayawada%2C%20Rajhmundry%2C%20Prakasam%2C%20Bapatla%2C%20Eluru%2C%20East%20Godawari%2C%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20Konasema%2C%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20Vizianagaram%2C%20Nellore%2C%20Tirupati%2C%20Kadapa%2C%20Anantpur%2C%20and%20Kurnool%20districts.%20The%20NIA%20said%20that%20the%20nine%20locations%20in%20Telangana%20include%20districts%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20Mahabubnagar%2C%20Hanumakonda%2C%20Ranga%20Reddy%2C%20and%20Adilabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20investigation%2C%20first%20registered%20and%20handled%20by%20the%20local%20state%20police%20in%202020%2C%20was%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20NIA%20in%202021.%20Popularly%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Munchingiputtu%20case%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20deals%20with%20alleged%20Maoist%20movement%20and%20literature%20in%20a%20village%20of%20the%20Alluri%20Sitharama%20Raju%3Cbr%3E%20district.%20The%20NIA%20has%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20seven%20persons%20in%20that%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20immediate%20causes%20for%20worry%20expressed%20by%20those%20raided%20is%20around%20the%20seizure%20of%20electronic%20devices.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20lawyers%20and%20researchers%20and%20very%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20their%20electronic%20devices%20for%20their%20work.%20%E2%80%9CSeizure%20of%20electronic%20devices%20including%20mobiles%20without%20even%20providing%20cloned%20copies%20to%20the%20owners%20amounts%20to%20immediate%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20precious%20work-related%20material%20and%20contacts.%20It%20leads%20to%20an%20overwhelming%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20HRF%20statement%20reads.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20confiscate%20these%20devices%20in%20such%20a%20sudden%20manner%20results%20in%20a%20stunning%20dispossession.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20a%20deprival%20of%20valuable%20property%20of%20the%20functionaries%20concerned%20but%20also%20of%20their%20right%20to%20livelihood%2C%20privacy%20and%20human%20dignity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696318456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06145703%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnia-raids-62-andhra-pradesh-telangana-maoist%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20raids%20were%20in%20connection%20with%20the%202021%20Munchingiputtu%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20conspiracy%20case.%20Devices%20and%20literature%20belonging%20to%20functionaries%20and%20lawyers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Association%20of%20People%20and%20Human%20Rights%20Forum%2C%20along%20with%20various%20other%20rights%20bodies%20were%20seized.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnia-raids-62-andhra-pradesh-telangana-maoist%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hema%20Malini%20marks%2020%20years%20of%20Baghban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696317720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104124892%2Cimgsize-25406.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbaghban-completes-20-years-hema-malini-says-aisa-lagta-hai-hum-abhi-shoot-karke-aaye-hain%2Farticleshow%2F104124969.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104124969.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHema%20Malini%20was%20assured%20that%20it%20won't%20be%20a%20typical%20'old%20woman'%20looking%20role%20and%20she%20would%20be%20portrayed%20just%20like%20she%20is%20in%20real%20life.%20She%20further%20said%20that%20it%20was%20BR%20Chopra%20sahab%E2%80%99s%20(producer)%20dream%2C%20to%20make%20this%20film.%20He%20gave%20her%20a%20narration%20before%20the%20shoot%20started.%20He%20was%20watching%20all%20the%20scenes%20from%20day%20one.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimes