%20conduct%20inquiries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fraid-on-newsclick-mumbai-police-conducts-searches-activist-teesta-setalvads-juhu-residence%2Farticleshow%2F104124675.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Journalists%20Raided%20Amid%20China%20Funding%20Row%2C%20Minister%20Says%20%26quot%3BNo%20Need%20To%20Justify%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20homes%20of%20several%20journalists%20associated%20with%20NewsClick%20were%20searched%20today%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20case%20under%20the%20stringent%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA).%C2%A0According%20to%20sources%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20had%20registered%20the%20case%20under%20the%20anti-terror%20law%20on%20August%2017%2C%20days%20after%20a%20New%20York%20Times%20investigation%20alleged%20that%20the%20news%20portal%20had%20received%20funding%20from%20a%20network%20pushing%20Chinese%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20searches%20today%20were%20conducted%20by%20officers%20from%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20at%20around%20two%20dozen%20locations%20in%20Delhi-NCR.%20No%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20so%20far%2C%20but%20sources%20said%20some%20journalists%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20police%20stations%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20media%20queries%20over%20the%20searches%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20said%20in%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20need%20to%20justify...%20If%20anyone%20has%20committed%20anything%20wrong%2C%20search%20agencies%20are%20free%20to%20carry%20out%20investigations%20against%20them%20under%20set%20guidelines...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20has%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20the%20raids.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Press%20Club%20Of%20India%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20multiple%20raids%20conducted%20on%20the%20houses%20of%20journalists%20and%20writers%20associated%20with%20Newsclick.%20We%20are%20monitoring%20the%20developments%20and%20will%20be%20releasing%20a%20detailed%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20multiple%20raids%20conducted%20on%20the%20houses%20of%20journalists%20and%20writers%20associated%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FNewsclick%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Newsclick%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20We%20are%20monitoring%20the%20developments%20and%20will%20be%20releasing%20a%20detailed%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20(%40PCITweets)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPCITweets%2Fstatus%2F1709056085578113381%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%203%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PCI%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20journalists%20and%20demands%20the%20government%20to%20come%20out%20with%20details.%20%23DefendMediaFreedom%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20news%20portal%20and%20investigated%20its%20funding.%20The%20central%20agency%20had%20also%20attached%20some%20assets%20linked%20to%20the%20news%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20case%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20relates%20to%20alleged%20violations%20in%20foreign%20funding%20and%20its%20use.%20The%20fresh%20FIR%20is%20based%20on%20information%20shared%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20earlier%20alleged%20that%20the%20news%20portal%20received%20a%20sum%20of%20nearly%20Rs%2038%20crore%20from%20entities%20linked%20to%20China%2C%20and%20how%20this%20amount%20was%20used%20is%20under%20the%20scanner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20have%20received%20salaries%20or%20remunerations%20from%20NewsClick%20are%20under%20the%20scanner.%20Laptops%20and%20phones%20of%20journalists%20whose%20homes%20were%20searched%20today%20have%20been%20seized%20for%20further%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20said%20more%20information%20about%20the%20searches%20will%20be%20shared%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20a%20New%20York%20Times%20investigation%20had%20alleged%20that%20NewsClick%20is%20among%20organisations%20that%20were%20funded%20by%20a%20network%20linked%20to%20US%20millionaire%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%20that%20pushes%20Chinese%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20portal%20and%20its%20sources%20of%20funding%20came%20under%20the%20scanner%20back%20in%202021%2C%20when%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20it.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20case%20was%20based%20on%20this%20case.%20The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20gave%20NewsClick%20promoters%20protection%20from%20arrest%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20now%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20portal's%20offices%20were%20also%20searched%20by%20Income%20Tax%20officers%20in%202021%20in%20an%20alleged%20tax%20evasion%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENewsClick's%20editor%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20had%20then%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20crackdown%20against%20the%20news%20portal.%20%26quot%3BThese%20investigations%20by%20various%20agencies%2C%20and%20these%20selective%20allegations%2C%20are%20attempts%20to%20stifle%20the%20independent%20journalism%20of%20media%20organisations%20-%20including%20NewsClick.%20The%20Constitution%20of%20India%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20guarantees%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%2C%20a%20right%20central%20to%20our%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20report%20in%20August%2C%20Mr%20Purkayastha%20had%20told%20The%20Indian%20Express.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20not%20new%20allegations.%20They%20hav