ok%20Over%20Union%20Carbide%20Has%20Court%20Date%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENearly%2039%20years%20after%20the%20Bhopal%20gas%20tragedy%20that%20killed%20thousands%20and%20affected%20many%20more%2C%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20US-based%20company%20that%20took%20over%20Union%20Carbide%20in%202001%20is%20set%20to%20appear%20in%20a%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20court%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Carbide%20Corporation%2C%20which%20owned%20the%20controlling%20stake%20in%20the%20Bhopal%20plant%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20gas%20leak%2C%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20Dow%20Chemical%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDow%20Chemical%20has%20consistently%20stressed%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bnever%20owned%20or%20operated%20the%20Bhopal%20plant%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20plant%20was%20owned%20and%20operated%20by%20Union%20Carbide%20India%20Limited%20(UCIL)%2C%20a%20Indian%20company%20in%20which%20Union%20Carbide%20(UCC)%20held%20just%20over%20half%20the%20stock.%20When%20UCC%20-%20itself%20a%20separate%20company%20from%20UCIL%20-%20became%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20TDCC%20in%202001%2C%20TDCC%20did%20not%20assume%20UCC's%20liabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20note%20on%20its%20website%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20those%20fighting%20for%20justice%20nearly%20four%20decades%20after%20the%20horrifying%20incident%20are%20looking%20at%20Dow%20Chemical's%20court%20appearance%20as%20a%20very%20significant%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERashida%20Bee%2C%20president%20of%20an%20organisation%20fighting%20for%20higher%20compensation%20for%20families%20affected%20by%20the%20gas%20disaster%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20last%2036%20years%2C%20a%20foreign%20accused%20will%20appear%20in%20court%20to%20respond%20to%20criminal%20charges%20of%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Disaster.%20This%20has%20been%20possible%20due%20to%20the%20support%20extended%20by%2012%20members%20of%20the%20US%20Congress%20in%20response%20to%20requests%20by%20our%20supporters%20in%20the%20International%20Campaign%20for%20Justice%20in%20Bhopal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%2012%20members%20of%20the%20US%20Congress%20wrote%20to%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20demanding%20that%20criminal%20summons%20be%20issued%20to%20Dow%20Chemical%20in%20connection%20with%20the%201984%20gas%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBalkrishna%20Namdeo%2C%20who%20leads%20another%20outfit%20representing%20the%20gas%20disaster%20victims%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20worst%20industrial%20disaster%20in%20history%2C%20the%20CBI%20in%201987%20charged%20Union%20Carbide%20with%20culpable%20homicide%20punishable%20by%20imprisonment%20of%2010%20years%20and%20fines.%20In%20February%201992%2C%20Union%20Carbide%20was%20declared%20a%20fugitive%20from%20justice%20by%20the%20Bhopal%20district%20court.%20By%20taking%20over%20Union%20Carbide%20in%202001%2C%20Dow%20Chemical%20committed%20a%20crime%20punishable%20by%203%20years%20of%20prison%20and%20fines%20under%20Section%20212%20of%20the%20IPC.%20They%20will%20now%20make%20their%20first%20appearance%20after%207%20summons%20from%20the%20Bhopal%20Court%20in%20the%20last%2018%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENawab%20Khan%2C%20who%20leads%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Peedit%20Mahila%20Purush%20Sangharsh%20Morcha%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20the%20CBI%20affirms%20that%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bsuccessor-in-interest%26quot%3B%20of%20Union%20Carbide%2C%20Dow%20Chemical%20is%20answerable%20to%20charges%20pending%20against%20Killer%20Carbide%20in%20the%20Bhopal%20District%20court.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20corporation%20is%20also%20answerable%20to%20charges%20under%20Section%20107%20of%20the%20IPC%20for%20abetment%2C%20as%20they%20facilitated%20the%20sales%20of%20Union%20Carbide's%20products%20in%20India%20even%20after%20the%201992%20court%20order%20of%20attachment%20of%20its%20properties%20in%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696315020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%