al%20body%20will%20take%20action%20tomorrow%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20police.%20Bharat%20was%20caught%20after%20a%20long%20investigation%20that%20involved%20reviewing%20footage%20from%20nearly%20700%20CCTV%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B30-35%20people%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20investigation.%20No%20one%20slept%20for%20three%20or%20four%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajay%20Verma%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Shockwaves'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2026%2C%20videos%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20showing%20a%20minor%20girl%2C%20haggard%2C%20bleeding%2C%20and%20begging%20for%20help.%20A%20CCTV%20camera%20on%20Badnagar%20Road%2C%20about%2015%20km%20from%20Ujjain%2C%20captured%20the%20girl%2C%20draped%20in%20rags%2C%20going%20door-to-door%2C%20seeking%20assistance.%20The%20chilling%20footage%2C%20that%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20country%2C%20showed%20people%20shooing%20the%20girl%20away%2C%20as%20she%20approached%20them%20one%20after%20the%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fujjain-rape-case-news-in-ujjain-rape-case-those-who-didnt-help-teen-may-face-charges-4436074%5C%22%3EIn%20Ujjain%20Rape%20Case%2C%20Those%20Who%20Didn't%20Help%20Teen%20May%20Face%20Charges%3A%20Police%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20minor%20girl%2C%20exhausted%20and%20traumatised%20with%20her%20body%20barely%20covered%20by%20a%20tattered%20cloth%2C%20aimlessly%20wandered%20the%20streets.%20Word%20of%20her%20agony%20reached%20an%20ashram%20not%20far%20from%20her%20location.%20A%20priest%20there%2C%20sensing%20that%20she%20had%20been%20sexually%20assaulted%2C%20draped%20her%20in%20a%20towel%20and%20rushed%20her%20to%20the%20nearby%20hospital.%20The%20medical%20examination%20confirmed%20her%20fears%3A%20she%20had%20been%20raped.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20girl's%20injuries%20were%20severe%2C%20so%20she%20was%20rushed%20to%20Indore%20for%20specialised%20medical%20care.%20Police%20officers%20volunteered%20to%20donate%20blood%20when%20she%20needed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20Bharat%2C%20was%20arrested%20three%20days%20later.%20The%20accused%20attempted%20to%20flee%20while%20reenacting%20the%20crime%20scene%20to%20collect%20evidence%2C%20including%20torn%20clothing%20but%20was%20swiftly%20caught.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20reached%20the%20spot%20to%20recover%20the%20clothes%20worn%20by%20the%20girl.%20Sensing%20an%20opportunity%2C%20Bharat%20Soni%20tried%20to%20escape.%20Police%20personnel%20chased%20and%20caught%20him.%20During%20this%2C%20he%20fell%20on%20a%20cemented%20road%2C%20injuring%20his%20arms%20and%20legs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Should%20Be%20Hanged'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBharat's%20father%20has%20called%20for%20the%20death%20penalty%20for%20his%20son%2C%20while%20the%20local%20bar%20association%20has%20urged%20its%20members%20to%20refuse%20to%20represent%20him%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20shameful%20act.%20Neither%20have%20I%20gone%20to%20hospital%20to%20meet%20him%2C%20no%20will%20I%20go%20to%20the%20police%20station%20or%20courts.%20My%20son%20has%20committed%20a%20crime%2C%20therefore%20he%20should%20be%20hanged%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20father%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERepercussions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20scheduled%20in%20November%20this%20year%2C%20vowed%20to%20prosecute%20the%20accused%20to%20the%20fullest%20extent%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20victim%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20We%20will%20take%20care%20of%20her%20in%20every%20way.%20She%20is%20my%20daughter%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20state's%20daughter%20and%20we%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20accused%20gets%20stringent%20punishment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fujjain-rape-father-of-man-accused-of-raping-12-year-old-in-ujjain-seeks-death-penalty-4437837%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BShe%20Could've%20Been%20My%20Child%26quot%3B%3A%20Ujjain%20Rape%20Accused's%20Father%20Seeks%20Death%20Penalty%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20horrific%20incident%20has%20provided%20additional%20fodder%20to%20opposition%20parties%20to%20question%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan-led%20state%20government%20which%20is%20under%20pressure%20for%20its%20dismal%20record%20on%20violence%20against%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20data%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20with%206%2C462%20cases%2C%20reported%20the%20most%20number%20of%20rape%20incidents%20in%20the%20country%20in%202021.%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Maharashtra%20have%20reported%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20cases%20of%20disappearance%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20between%202019%20and%202021.%20Of%20all%20the%20reported%20rape%20cases%2C%2050%20per%20cent%20were%20crimes%20against%20minors%2C%20NCRB%20data%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696313280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fkss3nbss_ujjain-rape-accused_625x300_30_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhouse-of-man-accused-of-raping-teen-near-ujjain-to-be-demolished-4444640%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20house%20of%20the%20man%20accused%20of%20raping%20a%20teenage%20girl%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Ujjain%20will%20be%20demolished%20tomorrow%2C%20as%20it%20was%20allegedly%20built%20illegally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhouse-of-man-accused-of-raping-teen-near-ujjain-to-be-demolished-4444640%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhouse-of-man-accused-of-raping-teen-near-ujjain-to-be-demolished-4444640%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhouse-of-man-accused-of-raping-teen-near-ujjain-to-be-demolished-4444640%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20More%20Patients%20Die%20At%20Maharashtra%20Hospital%2C%2031%20Deaths%20In%2048%20Hours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeven%20more%20patients%2C%20four%20of%20them%20children%2C%20died%20late%20last%20night%20at%20the%20government%20hospital%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Nanded%20that%20made%20national%20headlines%20yesterday%20following%2024%20deaths%20in%2024%20hours.%20This%20takes%20the%20death%20count%20in%20the%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%20Government%20Hospital%20in%20the%20past%2048%20hours%20to%2031.%20Among%20these%2031%20patients%2C%2016%20were%20infants%20or%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20condition%20of%20as%20many%20as%2071%20patients%20at%20the%20hospital%20is%20still%20critical%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Shyamrao%20Wakode%2C%20the%20dean%20of%20the%20hospital%2C%20has%20rejected%20allegations%20of%20medical%20negligence.%20He%20has%20also%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20or%20doctors%2C%20and%20stressed%20that%20the%20patients%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20treatment%20despite%20being%20given%20proper%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Medical%20Education%20Minister%20Hasan%20Mushrif%20is%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Nanded.%20Speaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20on%20my%20way%20to%20Nanded.%20This%20should%20not%20have%20happened.%20There%20was%20no%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20or%20doctors.%20We%20will%20investigate%20every%20death%2C%20and%20anyone%20found%20negligent%20will%20be%20punished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Maharashtra%20government%20official%20has%20said%20a%20committee%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20probe%20the%20deaths.%20%26quot%3BA%20three-member%20expert%20committee%20from%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%20district%20has%20been%20formed%20with%20a%20mandate%20to%20submit%20a%20report.%20I%20am%20personally%20visiting%20the%20hospital%20to%20review%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Dilip%20Mhaisekar%2C%20Director%2C%20Medical%20Education%20and%20Research%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20deaths%20in%20the%20government%20hospital%20have%20triggered%20a%20sharp%20attack%20by%20the%20Opposition%20on%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20has%20sought%20a%20detailed%20probe%2C%20saying%20the%20incident%20was%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20painful%2C%20serious%20and%20worrying%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Mr%20Kharge%20also%20referred%20to%20a%20similar%20incident%20at%20a%20government%20hospital%20in%20Thane%20in%20August%2C%20when%2018%20patients%20died%20within%20a%20short%20interval.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20targeted%20the%20BJP%2C%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20in%20Maharashtra.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20government%20spends%20thousands%20of%20crores%20on%20publicity%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20money%20to%20buy%20medicines%20of%20children%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20has%20said%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20should%20take%20up%20the%20matter%20and%20provide%20immediate%20help%20to%20the%20Nanded%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20yesterday%2C%20the%20hospital's%20dean%20had%20said%20the%2012%20newborns%20who%20died%20in%20the%20hospital%20on%20September%2030-October%201%20were%20in%20the%200-3%20days%20age%20group%20and%20had%20%26quot%3Bvery%20low%20weight%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20142%20admissions%20in%20the%20paediatric%20department%2C%20of%20which%2042%20are%20still%20critical.%20Oxygen%20and%20ventilator%20facilities%20are%20there.%20The%20patients%20are%20from%20neighbouring%20districts%2C%20including%20Hingoli%2C%20Parbhani%20and%20Washim.%20Some%20are%20from%20villages%20in%20neighbouring%20Telangana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmong%20the%2012%20adults%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20five%20were%20male%20and%20seven%20female.%20Four%20adults%20had%20heart-related%20ailments%2C%20one%20was%20suffering%20from%20an%20unknown%20poisoning%2C%20one%20had%20a%20liver%20issue%2C%20two%20were%20kidney%20patients%2C%20and%20one%20case%20was%20of%20complications%20during%20pregnancy.%20There%20were%20three%20accident%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Nanded%20district%20administration%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696313100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0gumjs4_nanded-hospital_625x300_02_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseven-more-patients-including-4-children-die-at-maharashtras-nanded-hospital-31-deaths-in-48-hours-4444466%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seven%20more%20patients%2C%20four%20of%20them%20children%2C%20died%20late%20last%20night%20at%20the%20government%20hospital%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Nanded%20that%20made%20national%20headlines%20yesterday%20following%2024%20deaths%20in%2024%20hours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseven-more-patients-including-4-children-die-at-maharashtras-nanded-hospital-31-deaths-in-48-hours-4444466%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseven-more-patients-including-4-children-die-at-maharashtras-nanded-hospital-31-deaths-in-48-hours-4444466%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fseven-more-patients-including-4-ch