n%20in%20the%20last%20year%20due%20to%20higher%20mortgage%20rates%2C%20but%20Zillow%20thinks%20it's%20a%20good%20time%20to%20buy%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20have%20the%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZillow's%20assessment%20is%20based%20on%20its%20analysis%20that%20a%20larger%20proportion%20of%20sellers%20are%20relenting%20on%20their%20asking%20prices%2C%20according%20to%C2%A0a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zillow.com%2Fresearch%2Ffall-housing-market-outlook-33122%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThursday%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20senior%20economist%20Jeff%20Tucker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20real%20estate%20company%2C%209.2%25%20of%20home%20listings%20saw%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fus-housing-market-outlook-home-prices-zillow-inventory-shortage-demand-2023-10https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fus-housing-market-outlook-home-prices-zillow-inventory-shortage-demand-2023-10%5C%22%3Eprice%20cut%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20week%20ending%20September%2016%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20share%20since%20November.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20about%20the%20price.%20Potential%20homebuyers%20also%20have%20many%20more%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20determined%20buyers%2C%20with%20enough%20budget%20room%20to%20accommodate%20the%20recent%20jump%20in%20mortgage%20rates%2C%20this%20fall%20is%20looking%20more%20and%20more%20like%20a%20sweet%20spot%3A%20There%20are%20more%20motivated%20sellers%20and%20more%20active%20listings%20overall%20than%20any%20time%20since%20last%20December%2C%20improving%20buyers'%20chance%20to%20find%20the%20right%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20Tucker%20wrote%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20home%20sales%20have%20slowed%20as%20houses%20have%20gotten%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fhousing-market-home-prices-ownership-costs-unaffordable-mortgage-payments-wages-2