3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20rug%20pull%20is%20a%20type%20of%20cryptocurrency%20scam%20in%20which%20developers%20of%20a%20new%20cryptocurrency%20project%20abandon%20the%20project%20and%20take%20investors'%20money%20with%20them.%20This%20can%20happen%20in%20a%20number%20of%20ways%2C%20such%20as%20by%20disappearing%20with%20the%20project's%20liquidity%2C%20disabling%20the%20project's%20website%20and%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20or%20making%20it%20impossible%20for%20investors%20to%20sell%20their%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFraudsters%20also%20dump%20their%20own%20tokens%20on%20the%20market%2C%20causing%20the%20price%20to%20plummet%20in%20the%20rug%20pull.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERug%20pull%20is%20basically%20derived%20from%20the%20English%20phrase%20to%20pull%20the%20rug%20out%20from%20under%20someone%2C%20means%20to%20remove%20support%20to%20somebody%20suddenly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERug%20pull%20is%20a%20major%20problem%20in%20the%20cryptocurrency%20industry%2C%20with%20billions%20of%20dollars%20lost%20to%20such%20scams%20each%20year.%20In%20fact%2C%20a%20recent%20report%20by%20Chainalysis%20found%20that%20rug%20pulls%20accounted%20for%20over%2036%20percent%20of%20all%20cryptocurrency%20scams%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20avoid%20rug%20pull%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20ways%20to%20avoid%20becoming%20a%20victim%20of%20a%20rug%20pull.%20The%20crypto%20investors%20need%20to%20be%20watchful%20about%20a%20few%20factors%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Do%20your%20research%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBefore%20investing%20in%20any%20cryptocurrency%20project%2C%20be%20sure%20to%20do%20your%20research%20and%20understand%20what%20the%20project%20is%20trying%20to%20achieve.%20Look%20at%20the%20team%20behind%20the%20project%20and%20see%20if%20they%20have%20a%20good%20track%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Be%20cautious%20about%20high%20returns%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Be%20wary%20of%20projects%20with%20high%20returns%20and%20low%20risk.%20If%20a%20project%20promises%20high%20returns%20with%20low%20risk%2C%20it's%20probably%20a%20scam.%20Cryptocurrency%20is%20a%20volatile%20asset%20class%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20guaranteed%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Social%20Media%20hype%20may%20not%20always%20be%20true%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Beware%20of%20projects%20that%20are%20heavily%20hyped.%20Scammers%20often%20use%20social%20media%20and%20other%20platforms%20to%20hype%20up%20their%20projects.%20Be%20wary%20of%20any%20project%20that%20is%20being%20heavily%20promoted%20without%20any%20substance%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Risk%20tolerance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Invest%20only%20what%20you%20can%20afford%20to%20lose.%20Cryptocurrency%20is%20a%20high-risk%20investment%2C%20so%20only%20invest%20what%20you%20can%20afford%20to%20lose.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696309260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fuaa53il_crypto_625x300_28_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Frug-pull-in-crypto-what-it-is-and-how-to-avoid-the-scam-4444475%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scamsters%20have%20defrauded%20thousands%20of%20people%20of%20an%20estimated%20Rs%20200%20crore%20across%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20by%20promising%20high%20returns%20in%20a%20short%20period%20through%20investment%20in%20crypto%20assets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Frug-pull-in-crypto-what-it-is-and-how-to-avoid-the-scam-4444475%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Frug-pull-in-crypto-what-it-is-and-how-to-avoid-the-scam-4444475%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Frug-pull-in-crypto-what-it-is-and-how-to-avoid-the-scam-4444475%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canal%2B%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Maxime%20Saada%20Details%20Long-T