20has%20been%20trying%20since%202009%20to%20build%20market%20share%20against%20Google%2C%20but%20Nadella%20said%20it%20could%20never%20compete%20against%20the%20search%20engine%20behemoth%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20its%20arrangements%20with%20Apple.%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20call%20it%20popular%2C%20but%20to%20me%20it's%20dominant%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadella%20told%20a%20Google%20lawyer%20during%20tense%20cross%20examination.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20The%20three-month%20trial%20is%20the%20biggest%20US%20antitrust%20case%20against%20a%20big%20tech%20company%20since%20the%20same%20department%20took%20on%20Microsoft%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20ago%20over%20the%20dominance%20of%20its%20Windows%20operating%20system.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Nadella%20broadly%20backed%20the%20government's%20contention%20that%20Google's%20intake%20of%20data%20from%20being%20the%20world's%20preeminent%20search%20engine%20created%20a%20network%20effect%20that%20only%20made%20Google%20a%20more%20powerful%20tool%20to%20advertisers%20and%20users.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BIt%20becomes%20even%20harder%20to%20break%20through%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20(market)%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadella%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0Defaults%20matter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Nadella%20said%20distribution%20was%20key%20to%20a%20successful%20search%20engine%20and%20that%20his%20company%20was%20prepared%20to%20pay%20Apple%20dearly%20to%20give%20Bing%20the%20default%20status%20on%20the%20iPhone.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BDefaults%20are%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20matters%26quot%3B%20and%20arguments%20by%20Google%20that%20users%20will%20easily%20switch%20to%20another%20app%20were%20%26quot%3Bbogus%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadella%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20a%20game%20changer%20(for%20Bing)%20to%20be%20a%20default%20on%20Safari%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Apple%20instead%20stuck%20with%20Google%20and%20receives%20billions%20of%20dollars%20every%20year%20from%20the%20search%20engine%20giant%20with%20a%20generous%20revenue%20sharing%20deal%2C%20earlier%20testimony%20has%20revealed.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20With%20his%20approaches%20rebuffed%20by%20Apple%2C%20Nadella%20said%20that%20Bing%20has%20remained%20a%20very%20small%20player.%3Cbr%3E%20The%20company%20has%20continued%20to%20invest%20in%20Bing%2C%20Nadella%20said%2C%20awaiting%20a%20possible%20%26quot%3Bparadigm%20shift%26quot%3B%20or%20some%20sort%20of%20government%20intervention%20to%20restructure%20the%20business.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20The%20CEO%20also%20testified%20that%20despite%20some%20early%20%26quot%3Bexuberance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20no%20longer%20believed%20the%20emergence%20of%20ChatGPT%20would%20reshape%20Google's%20dominance%20of%20the%20search%20business.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Microsoft%20earlier%20this%20year%20moved%20aggressively%20to%20integrate%20the%20AI%20technology%20into%20its%20Bing%20search%20engine%2C%20creating%20some%20expectation%20that%20Google's%20singular%20position%20was%20under%20threat.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Nadella%20said%20he%20was%20now%20worried%20that%20Google%20would%20be%20able%20to%20use%20its%20dominance%20in%20search%20to%20strongarm%20content%20providers%20that%20are%20key%20to%20training%20generative%20AI%20models.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BI%20worry%20a%20lot%20in%20spite%20of%20my%20enthusiasm%20that%20this%20vicious%20cycle%20can%20become%20even%20more%20vicious%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadella%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696307520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-04%2Fbloomberg-satya-nadella_650x400_71459564487.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-satya-nadella-hits-out-at-dominant-google-in-us-trial-4443969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A