him%20so%20successful%20in%20business%20did%20not%20magically%20shut%20off%20when%20he%20came%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%2C%20and%20the%20vast%20economic%20imbalance%20between%20us%2C%20meant%20that%20in%20the%20months%20following%20our%20wedding%2C%20a%20certain%20dynamic%20began%20to%20take%20hold.%20Elon's%20judgment%20overruled%20mine%2C%20and%20he%20was%20constantly%20remarking%20on%20the%20ways%20he%20found%20me%20lacking.%20'I%20am%20your%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20him%20repeatedly%2C%20'not%20your%20employee.'%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'If%20you%20were%20my%20employee%2C'%20he%20said%20just%20as%20often%2C%20'I%20would%20fire%20you.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20essay%2C%20his%20ex-wife%20said%20that%20Mr%20Musk%20pressurised%20her%20to%20colour%20her%20hair%20even%20blonder.%20The%20relationship%20was%20put%20under%20great%20strain%20after%20the%20loss%20of%20their%20first%20son%2C%20Nevada%2C%20to%20SIDS.%20She%20then%20gave%20birth%20to%20twins%20and%20triplets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNevada's%20death%20sent%20me%20on%20a%20years-long%20inward%20spiral%20of%20depression%20and%20distraction%20that%20would%20be%20continuing%20today%20if%20one%20of%20our%20nannies%20hadn't%20noticed%20me%20struggling%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20the%20essay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20got%20a%20divorce%20in%20September%202008.%20Elon%20Musk%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpagesix.com%2F2016%2F03%2F24%2Felon-musk-to-first-wife-if-you-were-my-employee-id-fire-you%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPage%20Six%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20had%20offered%20Justine%20a%20settlement%20%26quot%3Bequivalent%20to%20a%20pre-tax%20income%20of%20%2480%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20she%20rejected%2C%20and%20he%20pays%20all%20expenses%20for%20their%20kids%20plus%20%2420%2C000%20(after%20taxes)%20per%20month.%20She%20also%20got%20the%20family%20home%20in%20Bel%20Air.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3