%20comprehensive%2C%20fact-finding%20report%2C%20%3Cem%3ETekunia%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20Massacre%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20democratic%20rights%20activists%20from%20several%20organisations%20highlight%20details%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20socio-economic%20background%20of%20the%20region%2C%20and%20its%20political%20culture.%20What%20stands%20out%20are%20three%20key%20dimensions%20%E2%80%93%20the%20unresolved%20agrarian%20questions%2C%20the%20distortions%20of%20democracy%2C%20and%20the%20culture%20of%20impunity%20%E2%80%93%20which%20coalesce%20to%20render%20our%20democratic%20apparatus%2C%20its%20structures%2C%20processes%2C%20and%20culture%20ineffective%20against%20the%20rising%20tide%20of%20%E2%80%98electoral%20authoritarianism%E2%80%99%20in%20which%20violence%20against%20innocent%20citizens%20is%20legitimised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnresolved%20land%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20authors%20detail%20about%20the%20region%20that%20is%20underdeveloped%20economically%20and%20socially%20(with%20all%20its%20socio-economic%20parameters%20below%20the%20national%20average)%20also%20encapsulates%20the%20fall-out%20of%20the%20unresolved%20land%20questions.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20ecologically%20rich%20Tarai%20region%2C%20in%20which%20Sikh%20farmers%20were%20encouraged%20to%20settle%20and%20render%20productive%2C%20there%20are%20now%20economic%20and%20political%20tensions%20as%20to%20who%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98outsider%E2%80%99%20and%20who%20the%20%E2%80%98insider%E2%80%99.%20That%20such%20a%20region%20manifests%20all%20the%20key%20features%20of%20agrarian%20distress%20(over-indebted%20farmers%2C%20inadequate%20farm%20incomes%2C%20exhausted%20lands%2C%20etc.)%20also%20highlights%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20current%20dominant%20model%20of%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20farmers%20who%20had%20gathered%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20massacre%20were%20supporters%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20led%20by%20the%20Samyukt%20Kis