e-based-survey-ndtv-explains-4443519%5C%22%3Ecaste%20census%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20found%20that%2036%25%20of%20the%20state's%2013.1%20crore-strong%20population%20belongs%20to%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%2C%2027.1%25%20to%20Backward%20Classes%2C%2019.7%25%20to%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20and%201.7%25%20to%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20The%20general%20population%20accounts%20for%2015.5%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EYadavs%2C%20the%20OBC%20group%20to%20which%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20belongs%2C%20are%20the%20largest%20population%20group%20in%20Bihar%2C%20accounting%20for%2014.27%25%20of%20the%20total%2C%20according%20to%20the%20caste%20census%20survey.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EDalits%2C%20or%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20comprise%2019.65%25%20of%20Bihar's%20population%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20nearly%2022%20lakh%20(1.68%25)%20people%20from%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EChief%20Minister%20Kumar%20said%20that%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20survey%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20representatives%20of%20all%20nine%20state%20legislature%20parties%20that%20agreed%20to%20the%20survey%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fnitish-kumar%5C%22%3EBihar%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20declined%20to%20comment%20when%20asked%20by%20if%20the%20caste%20census%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20revival%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission's%20recommendations%2C%20triggering%20demands%20for%20revised%20caste%20quotas%20proportional%20to%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20not%20be%20proper%20for%20me%20to%20go%20into%20such%20details%20right%20now.%20Let%20me%20share%20the%20findings%20with%20all%20parties%20tomorrow.%20After%20that%2C%20our%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20making%20policies%20targeted%20at%20castes%20that%20may%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20in%20need%20of%20greater%20assistance.%20I%20must%20add%2C%20the%20survey%20will%20benefit%20all%20castes%2C%20without%20exception%2C%26quot%3B%20