gh%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20unable%20to%20even%20hold%20the%20routine%20decadal%20census%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20sends%20out%20a%20clear%20political%20signal%20that%20it%20can%20be%20done%20at%20an%20all-India%20level.%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20socio-economic%20caste%20%E2%80%98surveys%E2%80%99%20are%20ongoing.%20BJP%20will%20be%20harder%20pressed%20to%20explain%20why%20it%20cannot%20be%20done%20nationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E2.%20The%20Hindu%20%E2%80%98majority%E2%80%99%20argument%20takes%20a%20beating%20as%20this%20quantifies%20a%20sense%20of%20the%20real%20majority%20that%20exists.%20%3Cem%3ESanatan%20Dharm%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20is%20being%20pitched%20as%20a%20key%20weapon%20to%20attack%20the%20Opposition%20after%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20comments%20on%20it.%20Modi%20himself%20has%20led%20the%20attack.%20But%20this%20will%20be%20busted%20by%20the%20data.%20To%20the%20extent%20that%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20about%20maintaining%20caste%20hierarchies%20eternally%20(%3Cem%3ESanatan%3C%2Fem%3E).%20OBC%20%2B%20SC%20%2B%20ST%20%3D%2084%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FRahulGandhi%2Fstatus%2F1708788188142239822%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%20the%20Opposition%20as%20it%20did%20the%20math%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20force%20the%20BJP%20to%20rethink%20that%20route.%20A%20keen%20awareness%20of%20the%20massive%20caste%20divide%20fostered%20by%20caste%20numbers%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20a%20Hindu-Muslim%20one%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20would%20like%20to%20impose%20as%20the%20only%20one%2C%20spells%20trouble%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-caste-census-released-at-63-obc-ebc-groups-set-to-take-pole-position-in-state-politics%5C%22%3EBihar%E2%80%99s%20Much-Awaited%20Caste%20Census%20Puts%20OBC-EBC%20Groups%20at%20Politically%20Dominant%2063%25%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3.%20The%20Modi%20government%20went%20ahead%20in%202019%20with%20the%20controversial%2010%25%20Economically%20Weaker%20Section%20reservations.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsupreme-court-upholds-10-quota-for-economically-weaker-sections-no-violation-of-constitution%2Farticleshow%2F95348361.cms%5C%22%3Ejudiciary%20helped%20and%20waived%20off%20the%2050%25%20ceiling%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20it.%20With%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98General%E2%80%99%20(%3Cem%3Esaamanya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20read%20%E2%80%98upper%20castes%E2%80%99)%20category%20now%20getting%20revealed%20to%20be%20a%20mere%2015.52%25%2C%20and%20if%20extrapolated%20all-India%2C%20it%20is%20a%20tough%20call%20to%20defend%20why%20OBCs%20should%20be%20content%20with%20a%20relatively%20low%20percentage%20of%20the%20pie%2C%20so%20disproportionate%20to%20their%20share%20in%20population%20while%20the%20%E2%80%98General%E2%80%99%20get%20to%20have%20their%20cake%3F%20Essentially%2C%20who%20will%20defend%2C%2010%25%20for%2015.2%25%2C%20but%20only%2027%25%20for%2063.13%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20which%20is%20what%2036.01%25%20(Extreme%20Backward%20Castes)%20%2B%2027.12%25%20(OBCs)%20adds%20up%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4.%20In%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%20among%20OBCs%20has%20seen%20a%20sharp%20rise.%20To%20hold%20onto%20that%20is%20key%20to%20any%20hopes%20it%20may%20have%20of%20coming%20back%20to%20power%20in%20May%202024.%20Already%20nervous%20about%20the%20Opposition%20pivoting%20to%20turning%20into%20a%20wide%20network%20of%20OBCs%2C%20that%20too%20%E2%80%98non-dominant%E2%80%99%20OBCs%20as%20chief%20ministers%20and%20in%20the%20state%20leadership%20(Siddaramaiah%2C%20M.K.%20Stalin%2C%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%2C%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20to%20name%20just%20the%20chief%20ministers)%2C%20and%20with%20numbers%20now%20revealing%20the%20disparity%20between%20who%20has%20real%20power%20and%20who%20does%20not%2C%20keeping%20the%2044%25%20of%20the%20OBCs%20who%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%202019%20onside%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664098%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJoint%20opposition%20parties%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40kharge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20in%20very%20striking%20remarks%20put%20his%20caste%20identity%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98non-dominant%E2%80%99%20OBC%20in%20Rajasthan%20out%20upfront%20as%20he%20called%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgardener-governance-model-ashok-gehlots-poll-pitch-in-rajasthan%2Farticle67366683.ece%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emali%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20gardener%20model%20of%20good%20governance%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20where%20all%20kinds%20of%20flowers%20and%20flora%20flourish.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20re-emphasised%2C%20that%20of%20the%2090%20secretaries%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20only%20three%20are%20OBCs.%20Being%20the%20sole%20OBC%20party%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20keen%20to%20project%20itself%20becomes%20hard%20to%20prove%20once%20data%20on%20disparity%20is%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E5.%20The%20BJP%20has%20always%20called%20for%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esamrasta%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20harmonious%20stability%20and%20not%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Esamajik%20nyay%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20social%20justice%2C%20with%20its%20pitch%20to%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits%20being%20one%20of%20accommodation%2C%20but%20within%20the%20Hindutva%20framework.%20Such%20a%20stark%20contrast%20between%20numbers%20and%20where%20they%20stand%20in%20their%20share%20in%20power%20challenges%20%E2%80%98accommodation%E2%80%99.%20A%20call%20for%20justice%20becomes%20hard%20to%20bottle%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E6.%20The%20BJP%20had%20led%20from%20the%20front%20this%20year%2C%20calling%20for%20nixing%20reservation%20for%20Muslims%2C%20trying%20to%20whip%20up%20communal%20divides%20by%20making%20it%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20versus%20all%20else%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20arguing%20till%20as%20far%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20justify%20why%20reservation%20for%20Muslim%20backwards%20needed%20to%20be%20nixed.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20Bench%20asked%20tough%20questions%20which%20led%20the%20former%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20to%20freeze%20its%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Famit-shah-terms-muslim-quota-in-telangana-as-unconstitutional%2Farticle66770807.ece%5C%22%3Eon%20April%2024%2C%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20openly%20pitched%20for%20scrapping%20any%20quota%20for%20Muslim%20backwards%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D.%20But%20with%20cold%20numbers%20emerging%20on%20where%20the%20divides%20and%20disparities%20are%2C%20it%20would%20be%20tough%20to%20argue%20that%20Muslims%20are%20creaming%20off%20benefits%20meant%20for%20others.%20The%20BJP%20cannot%20be%20faulted%20for%20not%20trying.%20BJP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Jaiswal%20is%20quoted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fhindi%2Farticles%2Fc06r573kmmzo%5C%22%3Eby%20BBC%20Hindi%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Crightful%20due%20of%20Backwards%20has%20been%20cut%20into%20by%20Lalu%20and%20Nitish%20including%20%3Cem%3EKulhadiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EShershahbadi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20upper%20caste%20Muslims%20amongst%20Backwards%E2%80%9D.%20But%20Jaiswal%20hastened%20to%20add%20that%20it%20was%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20finance%20minister%20in%20the%20state%20who%20allocated%20Rs%20500%20crore%20for%20the%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmodi-caste-census-bihar-nitish-tejashwi-india%5C%22%3EWhy%20Is%20the%20Modi%20Regime%20So%20Worried%20About%20The%20Caste%20Survey%20in%20Bihar%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E7.%20The%20BJP%20had%20been%20hurt%20badly%20in%202015%20by%20Rashtriya%20Syawamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20expressing%20his%20feelings%20about%20reservation%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EOrganiser%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EPanchjanya%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20time%2C%20he%20has%20gone%20out%20of%20his%20way%20to%20say%20that%20the%20RSS%20is%20okay%20with%20caste%20reservations%20for%20as%20long%20as%20is%20necessary.%20But%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20caste%20sits%20very%20uneasily%20in%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20scheme%20of%20things.%20The%20divisions%20pointing%20to%20inequity%20and%20rank%20discrimination%20are%20not%20merely%20one%20of%20many%20faultlines%20in%20India%20but%20an%20essential%20feature%20of%20social%20and%20political%20life%20in%20the%20sub-continent.%20A%20caste%20census%20with%20numbers%20of%20socio-economic%20status%20makes%20the%20numbers%20hard%20to%20ignore%2C%20wish%20away%20or%20divert%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E8.%20Memories%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20in%20the%201990s%20(which%20recommended%2027%25%20reservation%20for%20OBCs%20in%20employment)%20and%20how%20it%20put%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekamandal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(call%20for%20Hindufication)%20on%20the%20back%20foot%2C%20forcing%20the%20BJP%20to%20rework%20its%20strategy%20spring%20to%20mind.%20There%20are%20two%20reports%20now%20under%20review%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%20looking%20at%20the%20central%20OBC%20list%20which%20has%20submitted%20its%20report%20and%20UP%E2%80%99s%20committee%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fjustice-kumar-commission-findings-remain-in-cold-storage-in-uttar-pradesh%5C%22%3Efour-member%20social%20justice%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20headed%20by%20retired%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20judge%20Justice%20Raghvendra%20Kumar%20to%20examine%20a%20division%20of%20the%20OBC%20quota%20appointed%20by%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20in%20May%202018%20waiting%20to%20be%20adopted%20or%20acted%20upon.%20Both%20called%20for%20%E2%80%98sub-categorisation%E2%80%99%20amongst%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ideological%20predecessor%2C%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20vociferously%20opposed%20%E2%80%98sub-categorisation%E2%80%99%20when%20Karpoori%20Thakur%20in%20Bihar%2C%20E.M.S.%20Namboodripad%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20Devraj%20Urs%20and%20others%20went%20ahead%20and%20introduced%20it.%20It%20is%20prevalent%20in%2011%20states%20at%20present.%20The%20BJP%2C%20as%20a%20smart%20tactic%2C%20may%20have%20wanted%20to%20consider%20this%20in%202017-18%2C%20to%20take%20down%20the%20%E2%80%98dominant%E2%80%99%20OBC%20castes.%20But%20now%2C%20with%20the%20political%20scenario%20changing%20dramatically%20after%20its%20re-election%20in%202019%2C%20and%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20total%20votes%2C%2048.9%25%20coming%20from%20across%20almost%20all%20OBCs%2C%20including%20so-called%20%E2%80%98dominant%20castes%E2%80%99%2C%20would%20it%20risk%20rocking%20its%20boat%20by%20%E2%80%98sub-categorisation%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E9.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%2C%20and%20a%20successful%20one%20so%20far%2C%20has%20been%20to%20divide%20OBCs%20as%20a%20category.%20It%20woos%20numerically%20smaller%20OBCs%2C%20but%20separately%2C%20to%20prevent%20a%20sense%20of%20a%20consolidated%20OBC%20group%20or%20Backward-Forward%20divide%20emerging.%20When%20such%20a%20divide%20emerged%20in%202015%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Assembly%20Election%20when%20Lalu%20and%20Nitish%20first%20came%20together%2C%20it%20led%20to%20the%20BJP%20shrinking%20to%20merely%2053%20seats%20in%20the%20Bihar%20Assembly%20and%20down%20to%20party%20number%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20emergence%20of%20numbers%20after%20a%20census%20is%20a%20significant%20move%20and%20will%20cause%20a%20disruption.%C2%A0It%20is%20worth%20watching%20out%20for%20it%20to%20unfold%2C%20going%20into%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696296659000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F25140601%2F2019_10img24_Oct_2019_PTI10_24_2019_000306B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnine-reasons-why-the-bihar-caste-census-could-shake-up-national-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20argument%20rests%20on%20Hindus%20accepting%20their%20place%20in%20the%20larger%20Hindutva%20tent%2C%20and%20the%20only%20dividing%20line%20to%20be%20one%20of%20against%20minorities.%20Caste%20numbers%20emerging%20could%20upend%20all%20that.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnine-reasons-why-the-bihar-caste-census-could-shake-up-national-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stephen%20Colbert%2C%20Jimmy%20Kimmel%2C%20Jimmy%20Fallon%20Celebrate%20Late%20Night%E2%80%99s%20Return%3A%20%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20Been%20a%20Long%20Time%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696296647000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FColbert-Kimmel-Fallon.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%