sed%20and%20that%20showed%20how%20sharp%20his%20concentration%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Rauf%20said%20in%20ESPNcricinfo's%20documentary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fcricket-videos%2Fthe-incredible-rise-of-haris-rauf-1400629%5C%22%3EThe%20Incredible%20rise%20of%20Haris%20Rauf%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20during%20practice%20sessions%20in%20the%20nets%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20playing%20a%20match%20against%20him%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20net%20bowler.%20His%20remarkable%20control%20and%20intensity%20made%20me%20realise%20why%20he%20has%20such%20a%20reputation%20in%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERauf%20also%20spoke%20about%20his%20admiration%20for%20South%20African%20pace%20legend%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dale%20Steyn%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F15-dale-steyn-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDale%20Steyn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20watch%20Dale%20Steyn%20and%20I%20liked%20the%20way%20he%20used%20to%20show%20aggression%20on%20the%20field%20after%20picking%20up%20a%20wicket.%20He%20inspired%20me%20to%20be%20aggressive%20on%20the%20field.%20That's%20why%20he%20is%20my%20idol%2C%26quot%3B%20Rauf%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696296000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fmtnjd8jo_virat-kohli-and-haris-rauf_625x300_02_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhen-i-was-net-bowler-for-indian-team-haris-rauf-on-early-duels-with-virat-kohli-4442165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Away%20from%20international%20cricket%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Haris%20Rauf%20have%20also%20faced%20each%20other%20in%20the%20nets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhen-i-was-net-bowler-for-indian-team-haris-rauf-on-early-duels-with-virat-kohli-4442165%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.o