rticleshow%2F104116992.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSanatana%20Dharma%20Is%20Only%20Religion%2C%20Rest...%26quot%3B%3A%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20Amid%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20controversial%20comments%20made%20by%20DMK%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20on%20Sanatana%20Dharma%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20has%20said%20that%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20the%20only%20religion%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20all%20are%20sects%20and%20methods%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20'Shrimad%20Bhagwat%20Katha%20Gyan%20Yagya'%20event%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSanatana%20Dharma%20is%20the%20only%20religion%2C%20the%20rest%20are%20all%20sects%20and%20methods%20of%20worship.%20Sanatan%20is%20the%20religion%20of%20humanity%20and%20if%20it%20is%20attacked%20then%20there%20will%20be%20a%20crisis%20for%20humanity%20across%20the%20globe%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Yogi%20addressed%20the%20final%20session%2C%20which%20marked%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20seven-day%20'Shrimad%20Bhagwat%20Katha%20Gyan%20Yagya'%20held%20at%20the%20Gorakhnath%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20held%20in%20remembrance%20of%20the%2054th%20death%20anniversary%20of%20Mahant%20Digvijay%20Nath%20and%20the%209th%20death%20anniversary%20of%20the%20national%20saint%20Mahant%20Avaidyanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Yogi%20further%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20an%20open%20mindset%20to%20understand%20the%20essence%20of%20Shrimad%20Bhagwat's%20narrow-minded%20perspectives%20and%20struggle%20to%20comprehend%20its%20vastness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20story%20of%20Bhagwat%20is%20boundless%20and%20cannot%20be%20confined%20to%20specific%20days%20or%20hours.%20It%20flows%20endlessly%2C%20and%20devotees%20continuously%20absorb%20its%20essence%20into%20their%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Monday%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%20%26quot%3BThe%20needs%20of%20the%20country%20and%20society%20are%20the%20priority%20of%20a%20saint.%20Mahant%20Digvijaynath%20ji%20was%20one%20such%20saint.%20He%20fought%20against%20the%20challenges%20of%20his%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20added%20that%20Mahant%20Digvijaynath%20belonged%20to%20the%20Rana%20clan%20of%20Mewar%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20who%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20the%20motherland%20while%20fighting%20for%20the%20self-respect%20of%20the%20country.%20He%20tried%20to%20do%20something%20new%20for%20society%20by%20getting%20involved%20in%20many%20religious%20and%20political%20rituals%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20added%20further%3A%20%26quot%3BMahant%20Digvijaynath%20ji%2C%20after%20joining%20Gorakshpeeth%2C%20first%20laid%20emphasis%20on%20education%20and%20established%20Maharana%20Pratap%20Education%20Council.%20To%20imbue%20the%20young%20generation%20with%20nationalism%2C%20he%20expanded%20his%20institutions.%20The%20Education%20Council%20established%20by%20him%20has%20contributed%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20university%20and%20has%20established%20its%20own%20university.%20Besides%2C%20by%20establishing%20four%20dozen%20educational%20training%20institutes%2C%20it%20is%20working%20to%20prepare%20the%20young%20generation%20to%20tackle%20challenges%20related%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696295640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fn53kob2_yogi-adityanath-pti-_625x300_01_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsanatana-dharma-is-the-only-religion-rest-all-sects-methods-of-worship-says-yogi-adityanath-4444162%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20controversial%20commen