0second%20to%20the%20US%20dollar's.%20In%20August%2C%20the%20greenback%20accounted%20for%2048%25%20of%20global%20payments%20via%20the%20SWIFT%20messaging%20system%20%E2%80%94%20way%20ahead%20of%20the%20euro's%20share%20at%2023%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20one%20other%20problem.%20India%20and%20China%20%E2%80%94%20the%20two%20biggest%20economies%20in%20the%20bloc%20%E2%80%94%20can't%20quite%20get%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20Jim%20O'Neill%2C%20the%20former%20Goldman%20Sachs%20chief%20economist%20who%20came%20up%20with%20the%20BRIC%20acronym%20in%202001%20(South%20Africa%20joined%20the%20bloc%20in%202010%20to%20round%20up%20BRICS)%20has%20been%20fielding%20interview%20questions%20about%20the%20proposed%20idea%20of%20a%20BRICS%20single%20currency%20on%20repeat%20mode%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20even%20get%20India%20and%20China%20in%20the%20same%20room%2C%20so%20the%20idea%20that%20they%20would%20commit%20to%20a%20shared%20currency%20and%20abandon%20their%20own%20domestic%20monetary%20policy%2C%20it's%20just%20kind%20of%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Neill%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20analysts%20also%20described%20relations%20between%20China%20and%20India%20as%20tense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EChina-India's%20terse%20relations%20are%20said%20to%20be%20a%20'pain%20point'%20in%20the%20BRICS%20bloc%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Beijing%20and%20New%20Delhi%20appear%20actively%20engaged%20with%20each%20other%2C%20the%20two%20counties'%20ties%20have%20been%20strained.%20In%20short%2C%20they%20appear%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fdefence%2Fworld-can-learn-from-frenemies-india-china-akbaruddin%2Farticleshow%2F63414400.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrenemies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20and%20India's%20relationship%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2FPortal%2FForeignRelation%2FChina_October_2017.pdf%5C%