6quot%3B%20in%202018%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2019%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbeyonce-netflix-deal-1203193729%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20paid%20%2420%20million%20for%20Beyonc%C3%A9's%20%26quot%3BHomecoming%26quot%3B%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20unknown%20if%20the%20streamer%20would%20still%20pay%20that%20kind%20of%20money%20for%20concerts%20%E2%80%94%20Netflix%20has%20been%20reining%20in%20its%20content%20spend%20%E2%80%94%20it%20doesn't%20really%20matter%2C%20as%20the%20pop%20stars%20stand%20to%20make%20a%20lot%20more%20money%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20unique%20moment%2C%20and%20these%20are%20unique%20artists%20who%20are%20recognizing%20the%20power%20of%20the%20movie%20theater%20to%20build%20buzz%20and%20generate%20revenue%2C%26quot%3B%20Dergarabedian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20%E2%80%94%20through%20a%20deal%20her%20parents%20brokered%20with%20AMC%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0is%20financing%20the%20production%20of%20%26quot%3BTaylor%20Swift%3A%20The%20Eras%20Tour%26quot%3B%20herself%20and%20putting%20it%20directly%20in%20theaters%2C%20with%20no%20studio%20middleman%20eating%20production%20and%20distribution%20costs%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpuck.news%2Fnewsletter_content%2Fwhat-im-hearing-taylors-movie-details-caas-auction-amazons-rebrand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuck's%20Matthew%20Belloni%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20273%20million%20Instagram%20followers%2C%20no%20expensive%20marketing%20is%20needed.%20(Though%20there%20was%20that%20commercial%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-travis-kelce-economy-nfl-eras-tour-2023-9%5C%22%3ETravis%20Kelce's%20football%20game%20on%20Sunday%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%2C%20herself%2C%20is%20the%20number%20one%20marketing%20tool%20that%20they%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Shawn%20Robbins%2C%20the%20chief%20analyst%20at%20Box%20Office%20Pro%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20theaters%20will%20get%2043%25%20of%20the%20gross%20ticket%20revenue%2C%20while%2057%25%20will%20go%20to%20the%20Swifts%20and%20AMC%2C%20which%20will%20serve%20as%20the%20distributor%2C%20Belloni%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20potential%20for%20a%20%24100%20million%20opening%20weekend%2C%20according%20to%20Box%20Office%20Pro%2C%20that's%20%2457%20million%20for%20Swift%20and%20AMC%20to%20share.%20Even%20if%20they%20split%20it%20down%20the%20middle%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20extremely%20unlikely%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Swift%20machine%20would%20go%20home%20with%20nearly%20%2430%20million%20from%20just%20one%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20paying%20filmmaker%20Sam%20Wrench%20and%20any%20production%20costs%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Belloni%20reported%20that%20these%20will%20amount%20to%20%2410%20to%20%2420%20million%20%E2%80%94%20profit%20is%20all%20but%20guaranteed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20Beyonc%C3%A9's%20deal%20have%20not%20come%20out%20yet%2C%20but%20it's%20safe%20to%20say%20she%20negotiated%20a%20similar%20deal%20to%20Swift's%2C%20as%20it%20is%20also%20a%20partnership%20with%20AMC.%20AMC%20declined%20to%20comment%20beyond%20an%20initial%20press%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20money%20will%20come%20to%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20and%20Swift%20down%20the%20line%2C%20when%20they%20offer%20their%20films%20on%20video-on-demand%20platforms%20and%20sell%20them%20to%20streamers.%20That%20cash%20will%20likely%20go%20directly%20into%20their%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20wonderfully%20translate%20to%20the%20small%20screen%20once%20they've%20had%20their%20theatrical%20runs.%20It's%20great%20for%20the%20movie%20theaters%3B%20it's%20great%20for%20the%20artist%2C%26quot%3B%20Dergarabedian%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20movies%20also%20push%20listens%20and%20downloads.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20the%20halo%20effect%20this%20can%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20makes%20the%20Eras%20and%20Renaissance%20movies%20so%20unique%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConcert%20films%20are%20nothing%20new%2C%20going%20back%20to%20%26quot%3BWoodstock%26quot%3B%20in%201970.%20%26quot%3BMichael%20Jackson's%20This%20Is%20It%26quot%3B%20grossed%20%24262.5%20million%20worldwide%20in%202009%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BJustin%20Bieber%3A%20Never%20Say%20Never%26quot%3B%20grossed%20%2499%20million%20in%202011%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Comscore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBets%20are%20that%20Swift%20and%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20can%20break%20records.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20not%20the%20first%20concert%20films%20to%20be%20released%20in%20theaters%2C%20but%20the%20way%20that%20they%20are%20releasing%20them%20and%20the%20audience%20they%20are%20going%20after%20is%20what's%20groundbreaking%2C%26quot%3B%20Robbins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Eras%20film%20will%20be%20released%20on%20over%204%2C000%20screens%20in%20North%20America%3B%20the%20Renaissance%20film%20likely%20will%20have%20a%20similar%20rollout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20doubt%20both%20films%20will%20perform.%20Many%20fans%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresale-price-taylor-swift-eras-tour-reputation-ticket-pitchfork-report-2023-8%23%3A~%3Atext%3DShe%2520told%2520Insider%2520that%2520while%2Cranged%2520from%2520%25245%252C000%2520to%2520%252430%252C000.%5C%22%3Eskip%20the%20concerts%20due%20to%20sky-high%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20simple%20lack%20of%20inventory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20there%20is%20a%20release%20that%20taps%20into%20the%20cultural%20zeitgeist%2C%20it%20gets%20people%20talking%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Robbins%20said%2C%20likening%20the%20Eras%20film%20to%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbie-blows-up-oppenheimer-with-275m-opening-weekend-report-2023-7%5C%22%3EBarbenheimer%26quot%3B%20this%20summer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3B