EAfter%20all%2C%20that's%20part%20of%20function%20of%20these%20decoys%20%E2%80%94%20to%20confuse%20and%20deceive%20the%20enemy%2C%20possibly%20prompting%20them%20to%20target%20and%20destroy%20the%20fake.%20That%20eats%20away%20at%20weapons%20stockpiles%2C%20burning%20ammunition%20or%20wasting%20one-way%20attack%20drones%20in%20a%20war%20that's%20already%20stressing%20the%20world's%20reserves%20and%20forcing%20allies%20to%20work%20double-time%20to%20meet%20demands.%20Ukrainian%20troops%20aren't%20the%20only%20ones%20possibly%20falling%20for%20decoys%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20drones%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650867fccd637c0019c6f1c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDJI%20Matrice%20300%20reconnaissance%20drones%2C%20bought%20in%20the%20frame%20of%20program%20'The%20Army%20of%20Drones'%20are%20seen%20during%20test%20flights%20in%20the%20Kyiv%20region%20on%20August%202%2C%202022%2C%20prior%20to%20being%20sent%20to%20the%20front%20line.%3Cp%3ESERGEI%20SUPINSKY%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20also%20deceived%20Russian%20forces%20with%20fake%20targets.%20Late%20last%20year%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20they%20began%20placing%20fake%20High%20Mobility%20Artillery%20Rocket%20Systems%20(HIMARS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-fake-wooden-rocket-launchers-russia-waste-missiles-report-2022-8%5C%22%3Emade%20of%20wood%20on%20the%20battlefield%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20drawing%20Russian%20fire.%20A%20senior%20Ukrainian%20official%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post%20that%20Russia%20had%20wasted%20valuable%20Kalibr%20cruise%20missiles%20on%20the%20decoys%20as%20they%20attempted%20to%20destroy%20the%20US-provided%20rocket%C2%A0artillery%C2%A0systems.%20Decoy%20Ukrainian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-making-decoy-