A%20lack%20of%20tank%20tracks%20in%20the%20dirt%20is%20unusual%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20how%20convincing%20a%20decoy%20howitzer%20is%20if%20it's%20oddly%20sitting%20alone%20in%20a%20field%20%C2%A0rather%20than%20in%20a%20realistic%20firing%20position%20with%20at%20least%20basic%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20fire%20with%20D-30%20artillery%20at%20Russian%20positions%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Klishchiivka%20as%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20continues%20in%20Donetsk%20Oblast%2C%20Ukraine%20on%20August%2012%2C%202023%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e3f034bd98a600197b6c4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20fire%20with%20D-30%20artillery%20at%20Russian%20positions%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Klishchiivka%20as%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20continues%20in%20Donetsk%20Oblast%2C%20Ukraine%20on%20August%2012%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EDiego%20Herrera%20Carcedo%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%20have%20demonstrated%20the%20ability%20to%20build%20credible%20fake%20systems%2C%20but%20as%20they%20get%20better%20at%20recognizing%20each%20other's%20dummies%2C%C2%A0the%20new%20challenge%20is%C2%A0making%20smarter%2C%20more%20sophisticated%20decoys%2C%20treating%20them%20as%20if%20they're%20the%20real%20thing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20already%20examples%20of%20both%20sides%20attempting%20to%20do%20that.%20In%20the%20video%20of%20the%20fake%20T-72s%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20two%20of%20the%20inflatables%20are%20positioned%20near%20shrubbery%20and%20wrapped%20in%20camouflage%20materials%2C%20suggesting%20an%20extra%20level%20of%20preparation%20to%20make%20the%20decoys%20look%20a%20little%20more%20real%2C%20though%20experts%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-inflatable-tanks