%20to%20heavy%20flow%20of%20patients%20%5Bincluding%5D%20from%20that%20of%20neighbouring%20districts%20of%20Telangana.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20always%20ensure%20that%20a%20patient%20does%20not%20lose%20his%20life%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20essential%20medicines%20at%20our%20hospital.%20In%20such%20situations%2C%20we%20purchase%20medicines%20from%20the%20local%20budget.%20We%20cannot%20deny%20that%20sometimes%20there%20may%20be%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20for%20non-essential%20ailments%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20hospital%20sought%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20the%20dean%E2%80%99s%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CEssential%20medicines%20are%20available%20in%20the%20hospital.%20The%20hospital%20has%20Rs%2012%20crore%20in%20funds.%20For%20this%20financial%20year%2C%20Rs%204%20crore%20has%20been%20approved.%20Other%20patients%20are%20being%20treated%20as%20necessary%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dean%20also%20said%20that%20due%20to%20some%20staff%20members%20being%20posted%20out%20of%20the%20hospital.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20some%20difficulty%20since%20various%20staff%20were%20being%20transferred%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%2012%20adults%20who%20died%2C%20four%20have%20died%20due%20to%20heart%20attack%2C%20and%20others%20have%20died%20due%20to%20accidental%20injuries%2C%20complications%20during%20delivery%20and%20kidney%20failure%20among%20other%20complications.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20have%20launched%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20government%20demanding%20answers%20on%20these%20deaths.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20medical%20facilities%20and%20staff.%20Many%20nurses%20were%20transferred%20and%20their%20replacements%20were%20not%20given.%