%20for%20years%20in%20Fresno%20County%20and%20Central%20Valley%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ELos%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-09-30%2Fin-fresno-sikhs-and-oaxacans-unite-to-pass-caste-discrimination-ban%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20had%20picked%20up%20steam%20since%20October%202022%20following%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flos-angeles-council-president-steps-down-after-audio-leak-racist-comments-2022-10-10%2F%5C%22%3Eleaked%20audio%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%202022%20in%20which%20three%20Los%20Angeles%20City%20Council%20members%20were%20heard%20making%20racist%20comments%20against%20Oaxacans.%20The%20incident%2C%20which%20outraged%20the%20members%20of%20the%20civil%20rights%20movement%20in%20the%20US%2C%20has%20also%20drawn%20renewed%20attention%20to%20the%20discrimination%20faced%20by%20Oaxacans%2C%20due%20to%20the%20casta%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20proud%20of%20our%20City%20for%20once%20again%2C%20raising%20the%20bar%20on%20civil%20rights%20protections%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fresno%20City%20Council%20vice-president%20Annalisa%20Perea%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffresno-in-california-becomes-second-us-city-to-ban-caste-discrimination-101696185015475.html%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20television%20network.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20acknowledge%20that%20discrimination%20won%E2%80%99t%20end%20overnight%2C%20our%20City%20took%20bold%20action%20by%20passing%20this%20anti-discrimination%20policy%20to%20strengthen%20civil%20rights%20protections%20against%20caste%20discrimination.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mexico%20was%20colonised%20by%20Spain%2C%20a%20system%20called%C2%A0%3Ci%3ESistema%20de%20Castas%20%3C%2Fi%3Ewas%20established.%20According%20to%20this%2C%20those%20born%20in%20Spain%20as%20considered%20%E2%80%9Cpure%20Spaniards%E2%80%9D%2C%20placed%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hierarchial%20order%2C%20followed%20by%20Spaniards%20born%20in%20Mexico.%20Oaxacans%2C%20who%20are%20indigenous%20peoples%2C%20are%20placed%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20hierarchical%20order%20alongside%20Blacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20colonial%20period%2C%20the%20Spaniards%20implemented%20this%20system%20that%20resembled%20very%20much%20the%20system%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ELA%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-09-30%2Fin-fresno-sikhs-and-oaxacans-unite-to-pass-caste-discrimination-ban%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gaspar%20Rivera-Salgado%20as%20saying.%20Rivera-Salgado%2C%20an%20Oaxacan%20American%2C%20is%20the%20director%20Center%20for%20Mexican%20Studies%20at%20UCLA%20and%20a%20board%20member%20at%20the%20Binational%20Center%20for%20the%20Development%20of%20Oaxacan%20Indigenous%20Communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESikhs%20in%20Fresno%20saw%20in%20the%20plight%20of%20Oaxacans%2C%20the%20discrimination%20and%20oppression%20faced%20by%20the%20members%20of%20lower%20castes%20from%20South%20Asia.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20groups%20have%20shared%20a%20common%20experience%20of%20inequity%20and%20being%20treated%20as%20less%20than%2C%20right%20away%20they%20can%20understand%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20pain%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3ELA%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20Deep%20Singh%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Jakara%20Movement%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20by%20Fresno%20City%20Council%20is%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20larger%20movement%20advocating%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20caste%20discrimination%20across%20California%20state.%20Although%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcalifornia-legislature-passes-anti-caste-discrimination-bill%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMarch%252023%252C%25202023.%2Con%2520Monday%2520(August%252028).%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20Senate%3C%2Fa%3E%20passed%20a%20Bill%20with%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20outlawing%20caste%20in%20May%20this%20year%2C%20it%20is%20still%20pending%20for%20an%20approval%20from%20governor%20Gavin%20Newsom.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20rights%E2%80%99%20bodies%20have%20been%20exerting%20pressure%20on%20Newsom%20to%20sign%20the%20Bill%20in%20order%20to%20make%20it%20a%20law.%20Thenmozhi%20Soundararajan%2C%20an%20Indian%20American%20Dalit%20rights%20activist%2C%20has%20been%20on%20a%20hunger%20strike%20for%20about%20a%20month%20demanding%20Newsom%20approve%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hindu%20nationalist%20groups%20in%20America%20have%20been%20opposing%20the%20latest%20Bill%20passed%20by%20the%20Fresno%20City%20Council%20and%20the%20movement%20and%20groups%20calling%20for%20laws%20at%20the%20federal%20level%20to%20identify%20and%20ban%20caste%20discrimination.%20According%20to%20them%2C%20such%20laws%20would%20%E2%80%9Csingle%20out%E2%80%9D%20the%20Hindu%20community%20as%20perpetrators%20of%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696265321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F22121433%2FFph8kZ-aIAApPPD.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fafter-seattle-fresno-becomes-second-us-city-to-ban-caste-discrimination%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Sikhs%20along%20with%20Oaxacans%20led%20the%20movement%20that%20eventually%20prompted%20the%20Fresno%20City%20Council%20to%20unanimously%20pass%20the%20Bill%20to%20outlaw%20caste.%20Oaxacans%20from%20Mexico%20are%20placed%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20'casta'%20hierarchical%20order%2C%20which%20is%20similar%20to%20caste%20system%20practiced%20in%20South%20Asia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fafter-seattle-fresno-becomes-second-us-city-to-ban-caste-discrimination%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Private%20sector%20must%20cover%2090%25%20of%20climate%20investment%20in%20Ems%2C%20says%20IMF%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696263611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F11%2Ffull%2F1681231162-5425.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fprivate-sector-must-cover-90-of-climate-investment-in-ems-says-imf-123100200955_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20IMF%20said%20phasing%20out%20coal%20is%20necessary%20to%20reach%20climate%20goals%2C%20though%20it%20is%20challenging%20as%20many%20EMDEs%20highly%20depend%20on%20coal%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fprivate-sector-must-cover-90-of-climate-investment-in-ems-says-imf-123100200955_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fprivate-sector-must-cover-90-of-climate-investment-in-ems-says-imf-123100200955_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fprivate-sector-must-cover-90-of-climate-investment-in-ems-says-imf-123100200955_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UEFA%20vice%20president%20'sorry'%20after%20voting%20for%20Russia's%20football%20return%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696260240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-karl-erik-nilsson-uefa_6306512.jpg%3F20231002172239%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fuefa-vice-president-sorry-after-sky-news-revealed-he-voted-for-russias-football-return-12975166%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20second%20in%20command%20at%20European%20football's%20governing%20body%20has%20apologised%20after%20Sky%20News%20revealed%20how%20he%20voted%20to%20end%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20Russia's%20teams%20competing%20in%20continental%20competitions%20-%20contradicting%20the%20strong%20stance%20of%20the%20Swedish%20sports%20body%20he%20leads.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fuefa-vice-president-sorry-after-sky-news-revealed-he-voted-for-russias-football-return-12975166%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fuefa-vice-president-sorry-after-sky-news-revealed-he-voted-for-russias-football-return-12975166%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fuefa-vice-president-sorry-after-sky-news-revealed-he-voted-for-russias-football-return-12975166%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar's%20Much-Awaited%20Caste%20Census%20Puts%20OBC-EBC%20Groups%20at%20Politically%20Dominant%2063%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F16191410%2F2022_8img15_Aug_2022_PTI08_15_2022_000050B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFollowing%20several%20months%20of%20administrative%20exercise%20amid%20severe%20political%20contestation%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%202%2C%20released%20the%20results%20of%20the%20caste%20survey%20conducted%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20data%2C%20the%20population%20of%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20in%20Bihar%20is%2027.13%25%20and%20that%20of%C2%A0%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBC)%20is%2036.01%25.%20Castes%20like%20Yadav%2C%20Kurmi%2C%20Kushwaha%2C%20etc.%2C%20are%20enumerated%20under%20the%20OBC%20category.%20Together%20OBC-EBC%20groups%20account%20for%2063%25%20of%20the%20state%20population.%20From%20the%20last%20caste%20census%20conducted%20in%201931%20by%20the%20British%2C%20the%20population%20of%20OBC-EBC%20groups%20has%20seen%20a%2010%25%20jump.%20It%20maybe%20noted%20that%20the%201931%20census%20was%20conducted%20in%20the%20then%20undivided%20India%2C%20including%20present-day%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20population%20of%20Yadavs%20is%20the%20highest%20among%20OBC%20castes%20in%20the%20state%20at%2014.26%25%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20core%20vote%20bank%20of%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD).%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20population%20of%20the%20Kushwaha%20caste%20is%204.21%25%20and%20that%20of%20the%20Kurmi%20is%202.87%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStatistics%20show%20that%20the%20population%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%20in%20Bihar%20is%2019.65%25%20and%20that%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20is%201.68%25.%C2%A0The%20population%20of%20general%20or%20upper%20caste%20groups%20has%20come%20out%20to%20be%2015.52%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20upper%20castes%2C%20the%20population%20of%20Brahmins%20is%20the%20highest%20at%203.65%25.%20The%20population%20of%20Rajputs%20stands%20at%203.45%25%20and%20the%20Bhumihars%20population%20at%202.86%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCaste%20census%20was%20approved%20by%20all%20parties.%20It%20has%20not%20only%20revealed%20the%20population%20of%20castes%20but%20also%20their%20economic%20conditions.%20On%20this%20basis%2C%20further%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20for%20the%20development%20and%20upliftment%20of%20all%20sections%2C%E2%80%9D%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20and%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20welcomed%20the%20data%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Caste%20Census%20of%20Bihar%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20OBCs%2C%20SCs%2C%20and%20ST%20constitute%2084%25%20of%20its%20population.%20Out%20of%2090%20secretaries%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%2C%20only%20three%20are%20OBC%2C%20who%20handle%20only%205%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20budget.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20know%20the%20caste%20statistics%20of%20India.%20The%20greater%20the%20population%2C%20the%20greater%20the%20rights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20RJD%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20Bihar%20since%20it%20was%20in%20opposition.%20Chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20been%20on%20the%20same%20path.%20Four%20years%20ago%2C%20on%20February%2018%2C%202019%2C%20the%20proposal%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Legislature%2C%20when%20JDU%20and%20BJP%20were%20together.%20RJD%20and%20JDU%20were%20demanding%20caste-based%20enumeration%20in%20the%20entire%20country%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20had%20also%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20reaction%20on%20this%2C%20so%20caste%20enumeration%20was%20done%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20decision%20was%20taken.%20Meanwhile%2C%20JDU%20left%20the%20BJP%20and%20formed%20the%20government%20with%20RJD%20and%20caste%20census%20process%20were%20fastened.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20of%20the%20caste%20census%20started%20on%20April%2015%20this%20year%20and%20all%20the%20data%20was%20collected%20on%20August%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCaste%20enumeration%20was%20done%20in%20two%20phases%2C%20in%20which%20house%20listing%20was%20done%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20and%20caste%20enumeration%20of%20all%20the%20persons%20was%20done%20in%20the%20second%20phase.%20To%20ensure%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20data%2C%20we%20did%20random%20scrutiny%20of%20five%20percent%20of%20the%20data%20and%20prepared%20the%20final%20report.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20organisations%20and%20individuals%20had%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20to%20stop%20the%20caste%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPublic%20interest%20litigations%20(PIL)%20were%20filed%20against%20the%20caste%20census%20in%20Patna%20high%20court%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20Justice%20Madhuresh%20Prasad%2C%20while%20hearing%20the%20PILs%2C%20had%20put%20an%20interim%20stay%20and%20fixed%20July%203%20for%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20on%20August%201%20had%20upheld%20the%20caste%20survey%20dismissing%20petitions%20filed%20against%20it.%C2%A0Petitioners%20then%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2021%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20told%20the%20petitioners%20that%20it%20would%20not%20stay%20the%20exercise%20unless%20they%20made%20out%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20petitioners%20had%20argued%20that%20legally%20the%20caste%20census%20can%20not%20be%20conducted%20by%20the%20state%20government%20as%20only%20the%20central%20government%20has%20the%20right%20to%20do%20so%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20allowed%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20representing%20the%20Centre%2C%20to%20file%20its%20response%20on%20the%20issue%20within%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20questioning%20the%20caste%20census.%20The%20affidavit%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20other%20body%20under%20the%20Constitution%20or%20otherwise%20is%20entitled%20to%20conduct%20the%20exercise%20of%20either%20census%20or%20any%20action%20akin%20to%20census.%E2%80%9D%20But%20later%20it%20filed%20a%20fresh%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20withdrawing%20the%20paragraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20figures%20will%20set%20a%20benchmark%20for%20the%20country%20in%20giving%20representation%20to%20deprived%20and%20oppressed%20sections%20and%20the%20poor%20as%20per%20their%20population%20and%20to%20make%20policies%20for%20their%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20political%20fallout%20of%20census%20data%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20The%20government%20has%20released%20the%20data%20of%20a%20total%20of%20209%20castes%20in%20Bihar.%20Earlier%20the%20figures%20of%20these%20castes%20were%20estimated%20as%20the%20last%20caste%20census%20was%20done%20in%20the%201930s.%20But%2C%20now%20that%20their%20official%20numbers%20have%20come%20out%2C%20efforts%20will%20be%20made%20to%20create%20political%20vote%20banks%20according%20to%20the%20population%20of%20these%20castes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Naval%20Kishore%20Chaudhary%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20caste%20census%20has%20been%20conducted%20so%20that%20the%20castes%20can%20be%20consolidated.%20Now%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20these%20figures%2C%20parties%20representing%20different%20castes%20will%20demand%20reservation.%20Caste%20enumeration%20is%20completely%20a%20political%20move.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20population%20of%20the%20OBC%20group%20and%20EBC%20group%20is%2063%25%2C%20which%20is%20most%20important%20from%20the%20election%20point%20of%20view.%20Yadavs%20also%20have%20the%20largest%20population%20among%20OBCs%2C%20about%2014.26%25.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20population%20of%20Muslims%20is%20about%2017.70%25.%20Together%20the%20figure%20comes%20to%2031%25%20and%20both%20are%20considered%20core%20vote%20banks%20of%20RJD%2C%20so%20electorally%20RJD%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20a%20strong%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20votes%20of%20EBC%20castes%20are%20scattered%20among%20small%20political%20parties%2C%20so%20political%20parties%20will%20now%20try%20to%20mobilise%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Nai%20caste%20population%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20negligible%20but%20the%20census%20has%20revealed%20their%20population%20at%201.56%25.%20Similarly%2C%20Dusadh%2C%20Dhari%20and%20Dharahi%20castes%20had%20no%20estimated%20figure%20but%20current%20data%20revealed%20their%20population%20at%205.31%20percent%20whereas%20Chamar%20caste%20population%20stands%20at%205.25%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatna-based%20journalist%20Dipak%20Mishra%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20small%20castes%20had%20no%20bargaining%20power%20as%20they%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20negligible%20in%20numbers.%20But%2C%20now%20they%20have%20data%20so%20they%20will%20bargain%20and%20political%20parties%20will%20also%20try%20to%20accommodate%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20RJD%20leader%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20%E2%80%9CBased%20on%20these%20data%2C%20we%20will%20make%20the%20next%20election%20strategies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20seen%20in%20terms%20of%20population%2C%20the%20latest%20figures%20remain%20around%20the%20earlier%20estimated%20figures.%20The%20figures%20that%20have%20been%20reported%20so%20far%20regarding%20the%20population%20of%20OBC%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Upper%20Caste%2C%20etc.%20are%20almost%20similar%20to%20the%20figures%20obtained%20in%20this%20calculation.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20political%20analysts%20do%20not%20see%20the%20possibility%20that%20these%20figures%20will%20yield%20any%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Mahendra%20Suman%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20figures%20that%20have%20just%20come%20confirm%20the%20earlier%20estimates.%20Yes%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20earlier%20we%20had%20estimated%20figures%20and%20now%20we%20have%20official%20figures.%20So%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20the%20political%20significance%20of%20these%20figures.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20questions%20will%20be%20raised%20about%20Yadav%20and%20Rajput%2C%20whose%20population%20is%2014.26%25%20and%203.45%25%2C%20because%20in%20the%202015%20and%202020%20assembly%20elections%2C%20these%20two%20castes%20and%20some%20other%20dominant%20castes%20were%20given%20much%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20population%20and%20they%20also%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRJD%20and%20JDU%20cannot%20take%20any%20benefit%20from%20these%20figures%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20population%20alone%2C%20rather%20questions%20will%20be%20raised%20on%20them%20that%20they%20do%20not%20give%20tickets%20as%20per%20population.%20Yes%2C%20if%20the%20report%20of%20socioeconomic%20conditions%20of%20these%20castes%20is%20released%2C%20it%20will%20benefit%20them%20because%20these%20data%20will%20tell%20what%20is%20the%20social%20status%20of%20the%20castes%20and%20accordingly%20reservation%20demand%20will%20be%20intensified%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Dipak%20Mishra%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20may%20help%20RJD%20and%20JDU%20to%20some%20extent%20but%20the%20situation%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20of%20the%20Mandal%20era%20of%2090s%2C%20what%20RJD%20is%20expecting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYadav%20and%20Muslims%20were%20together%20about%2033%25%20but%20RJD%20had%20to%20lose%20in%202005%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696259119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F16191410%2F2022_8img15_Aug_2022_PTI08_15_2022_000050B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-caste-census-released-at-63-obc-ebc-groups-set-to-take-pole-position-in-state-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Together%2C%20OBCs%2C%20EBCs%2C%20SCs%2C%20and%20STs%20account%20for%2084%25%20of%20the%20state%20population.%20At%2014.26%25%2C%20Yadavas%20are%20numerically%20preponderant%20group%20among%20OBCs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-caste-census-released-at-63-obc-ebc-groups-set-to-take-pole-position-in-state-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Something's%20not%20right'%3A%20Family%20seeks%20answers%20after%20British%20man's%20death%20in%20Vietnam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696255260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F70x70%2Fskynews-vietnam-darren-blair_6306113.jpg%3F20231002121358%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnottingham-family-seeks-answers-over-british-mans-death-in-vietnam-12975111%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20family%20of%20a%20British%20man%20have%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe