n%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201987%2C%20former%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20constituted%20a%20committee%20for%20the%20National%20Perspective%20Plan%20for%20Women.%20This%20committee%20was%20led%20by%20union%20minister%20Margaret%20Alva%20and%20proposed%20reservations%20in%20rural%20and%20local%20body%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20drafted%20by%20this%20committee%20of%20women%20parliamentarians%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Alva%2C%20Geeta%20Mukherjee%2C%20Susheela%20Gopalan%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F214827%2Fvalentines-day-love-letters-emergency-madhu-pramila-dandavate-history-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPramila%20Dandavate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Dr%20Ranjana%20Kumari%2C%20who%20has%20also%20been%20fighting%20for%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20for%20more%20than%20two%20decades%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EFeminism%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20%5Bthese%20women%5D%20went%20around%20the%20country%20%5Band%5D%20sought%20opinions%20about%20the%20Bill%20and%20drafted%20it.%20I%20was%20one%20of%20the%20young%20scholars%20who%20helped%20in%20the%20process.%20It%20was%20their%20wisdom%2C%20and%20I%20put%20it%20in%20words.%20We%20eventually%20formed%20the%20%E2%80%98Seven%20Sisters%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20seven%20major%20national%20organisations%20of%20women%20came%20together%20and%20started%20campaigning%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20harbinger%20for%20change%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20were%20the%20local%20administrative%20bodies.%20In%201992%20and%201993%2C%20two%20bills%20were%20passed%2C%20which%20reserved%2033%20percent%20of%20seats%20and%20chairperson%20posts%20for%20women%20in%20rural%20and%20local%20body%20elections%20during%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20as%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3