D-led%20government%20introduced%2025%20percent%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Epanchayats%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Women%20proved%20to%20be%20better%20representatives%20than%20men.%20I%20think%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20Parliament%20will%20definitely%20improve%20as%20more%20women%20come%20in.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20performance%20has%20been%20far%20better%20and%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20less%20corrupt%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pramila%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Together%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%2012%20September%201996%2C%20the%2081st%20Constitutional%20Amendment%20Bill%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%20sought%20to%20introduce%2033%20percent%20reservation%20for%20women.%20Multiple%20reports%20state%20that%20it%20was%20Pramila%20Dandavate%20who%20tabled%20this%20bill.%20The%20Bill%20was%20referred%20to%20a%20joint%20committee%20which%20submitted%20a%20recommendation%20in%20December%201996.%20However%2C%20it%20lapsed%20after%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20H%20D%20Deve%20Gowda%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20then%20tabled%20in%201997%20under%20the%20I%20K%20Gujral%20government%2C%20but%20lapsed%20again%2C%20and%20was%20introduced%20in%201998%2C%201999%2C%202002%2C%20and%202003%20during%20the%20NDA%20government%2C%20but%20lapsed%20each%20time.%20There%20was%20some%20progress%20in%202008%20during%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20UPA%20government.%20The%20Bill%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20It%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Upper%20House%20in%202010.%20It%20finally%20saw%20the%20light%20of%20day%20on%2019%20September%202023%2C%20as%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20passed%20it%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Women%20are%20creators%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22ht