re%20given%20very%20few%20tickets%20even%20though%20they%20had%20participated%20in%20the%20struggle%20for%20democracy%20under%20Jaiprakash%20Narayan.%20Since%20then%2C%20I%20have%20become%20a%20consistent%20supporter%20of%20reservation%20for%20women%2C%20including%20in%20the%20Parliament.%20I%20feel%20that%20our%20party%20wants%20women%20to%20be%20decorative%20pieces%2C%20like%20%3Cem%3Eachar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pickle)%20with%20food%20or%20a%20flower%20pot.%20They%20do%20not%20want%20to%20share%20power%20in%20the%20real%20sense%20of%20the%20word%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pramila%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Together%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Uma%20Bharti%20said%20to%20the%20same%20publication%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20principle%2C%20I%20am%20against%20reservation%20because%20I%20believe%20that%20women%20should%20come%20forward%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20own%20merit%20and%20hard%20work.%20But%20my%2012%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20politics%20have%20led%20me%20to%20believe%20that%20this%20does%20not%20happen.%20Women%20rarely%20manage%20to%20come%20forward%20and%20when%20they%20try%20to%20do%20so%2C%20their%20own%20colleagues%20brand%20them%20as%20loose-characters.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20women%20will%20come%20into%20politics%20only%20if%20a%20reservation%20policy%20is%20implemented.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPramila%20joined%20hands%20with%20women%20across%20political%20parties%20to%20make%20this%20Bill%20a%20reality.%20She%20worked%20with%20Geeta%20Mukherjee%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Meira%20Kumar%2C%20Sumitra%20Mahajan%2C%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%2C%20and%20Hannan%20Mollah%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20610px)%20100vw%2C%20610px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fwomens-bill-1695994430.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Leaders%20from%20different%20political%20parties%20celebrating%20passage%20of%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20in%202010.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22610%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fwomens-bill-1695994430.jpg%20610w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fwomens-bill-1695994430-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fwomens-bill-1695994430-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fwomens-bill-1695994430-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331338%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22343%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESushma%20Swaraj%2C%20Brinda%20Karat%2C%20and%20Najma%20Heptulla%20celebrating%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20bill%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20travelled%20across%20the%20country%20to%20assess%20the%20ground%20realities.%20This%20committee%2C%20led%20by%20Mukherjee%2C%20made%20seven%20recommendations%2C%20which%20included%20reservation%20for%20a%20period%20of%2015%20years%2C%20and%20sub-reservation%20of%20Anglo-Indians.%20Five%20of%20these%20recommendations%20have%20been%20made%20a%20reality%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPramila%20also%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20amend%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315357%2Fmanilal-doctor-revolutionary-leader-freed-indentured-indian-labourers-in-fiji-mauritius%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnti-dowry%20and%20Sati%20Prevention%20Acts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20highlighting%20her%20dedication%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights.%20She%20campaigned%20against%20dowry%20killings%20and%20the%20practice%20of%20%3Cem%3ESati%3C%2Fem%3E%20(where%20a%20widow%20would%20end%20her%20life%20by%20jumping%20into%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20pyre)%20and%20was%20instrumental%20in%20bringing%20about%20the%20Amendment%20to%20the%20Dowry%20Prohibition%20Act%20and%20the%20Sati%20Prohibition%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20political%20activism%20led%20to%20her%2018-month%20imprisonment%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20She%20established%20the%20Mahila%20Dakshata%20Samiti%20and%20co-authored%20%E2%80%9CWidows%2C%20Abandoned%20and%20Destitute%20Women%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%20with%20Jamila%20Verghese%20and%20Dr%20Kumari.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20died%20on%2031%20December%202001%2C%20much%20before%20she%20could%20realise%20the%20fruits%20of%20her%20efforts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20legislation%20will%20bear%20fruit%20only%20in%202029%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20delimitation%20clause%20in%20the%20bill.%20The%20reservation%20is%20proposed%20to%20be%20implemented%20after%20a%20new%20census%20is%20published%20and%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20is%20completed.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20Pramila%E2%80%99s%20dream%20of%20seeing%20a%20third%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20filled%20with%20women%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20six%20more%20years.%20But%2C%20the%2046.1%20crore%20female%20voters%20will%20have%20something%20to%20look%20forward%20to%20in%20the%202029%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnnecessary%20conflicts%20that%20are%20a%20drain%20on%20our%20resources%20will%20stop.%20We%20are%20creators%2C%20not%20destroyers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pramila.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpramila-dandavate-first-woman-leader-tabled-women-reservation-bill-lok-sabha%23read-more%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Pramila%20Dandavate%20%E2%80%94%20The%20First%20Woman%20to%20Table%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20in%201996%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Aliza%20Noor%20for%20T