idth%2C%20how%20susceptible%20they%20are%20to%20diseases%2C%20and%20which%20tree%20needs%20aid.%20After%20covering%20Kashmir%2C%20we%20will%20move%20to%20Chenab%20valley%20in%20Jammu%20to%20geotag%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E.%20So%20far%20we%20have%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20these%20trees%20in%20the%20valley%20are%20diseased%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Syed%20Tariq%2C%20researcher%20and%20coordinator%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20census%20project%20of%20the%20institute%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20have%20also%20created%20a%20record%20form%20to%20catalogue%20each%20tree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20institute%20is%20now%20proposing%20to%20create%20an%20online%20database%20of%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20trees%2C%20they%20are%20also%20taking%20various%20revival%20measures%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20building%20nurseries%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%20can%20be%20cultivated%20on%20a%20mass%20scale%20and%20taking%20prompt%20action%20to%20cure%20the%20diseased%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20database%20is%20aimed%20at%20tracking%20the%20trees%E2%80%99%20health%20and%20growth.%20We%20are%20also%20raising%20awareness%20through%20social%20media%20campaigns%20and%20growing%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20tree%20saplings%20to%20increase%20their%20number%20in%20the%20valley%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tariq%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201075px)%20100vw%2C%201075px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F1W4A4996_11zon_11zon-1695975468.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221075%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khan%20is%20making%20room%20for%20the%20chinar%20sapling%20to%20grow%20well.%20Other%20young%20saplings%20planted%20by%20him%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F1W4A4996_11zon_11zon-1695975468.jpg%