0This%20flagship%20programme%20fosters%20a%20culture%20of%20creativity%20and%20innovative%20thinking%20among%20school%20children%20aged%2010-15%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThings%20were%20now%20looking%20up%20and%20Aditya%20decided%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20ISEF%202022%20(International%20Science%20and%20Engineering%20Fair)%20which%20is%20also%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20international%20pre-college%20science%20competition.%20But%2C%20he%20recounts%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20apply.%20A%20prerequisite%20was%20to%20first%20compete%20in%20the%20IRIS%20National%20Fair%20held%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20disappointment%20led%20him%20to%20another%20revelation.%20Despite%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304574%2Fscientist-builds-ai-enabled-device-to-diagnose-diseases-pathology-sigtuple-medtech-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escores%20of%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20funding%20available%20for%20student%20innovators%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20information%20available%20on%20these.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20isn%E2%80%99t%20there%20a%20platform%20where%20all%20of%20this%20is%20consolidated%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20thought.%20Then%20he%20decided%20to%20create%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Aditya%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Kalam%E2%80%99%20helps%20students%20in%20accessing%20the%20assistance%20they%20require%20to%20bring%20their%20ideas%20to%20fruition.%20As%20for%20the%20intent%20behind%20the%20name%2C%20it%20has%20a%20dual%20purpose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20was%20the%20inspiration%20of%20Dr%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20who%20spent%20his%20entire%20life%20advancing%20our%20knowledge%20of%20science.%20He%20served%20as%20a%20role%20model%20to%20millions%20of%20young%20students%2C%20including%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20meaning%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20is%20borrowed%20from%20the%20Hi